Amalungu endlu yowiso-mthetho yaseWales axhalabile ukuba  aya kwaziwa ngokuba ziiMuppets
Amalungu aliqela endlu avakalise ukothuka ngenxa yesindululo sokutshintsha isihloko sakhe sibe yi-MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament, ilungu lepalamente yaseWales).
Le ngxabano iye yavela kwingcambu yesicwangciso sokutshintsha igama leNdibano kwiPalamente yaseWales.
Amalungu endibano aphuma kuwo onke amaqela ezopolitiko aye abonisa inkxalabo yokuba eli nyathelo linokuba sisingcikivo.
Ilungu lebhunga leqela labasebenzi lathi iqela lakhe lalikhathazekile kukuba i-MWP yayihambelana neTwp okanye iPwp.
Kubafundi abangengawo amaWelsh: NgesiWelsh, twp ithetha isidenge kwaye, pwp, ilindle.
Ilungu lebhunga leqela iPlaid Cymru liye lathi iqela lakhe liphela aliyiboni kakuhle le nto kwaye linikeze ezinye iindlela.
Kwelinye icala, ilungu elingumgcini weWelsh lathi iqela lakhe lalivulekile xa lijonga igama elitsha, kodwa lathi kukho umahluko omncinci kakhulu phakathi kwegama elithi MWP nelithi Muppet.
Kule meko, kufuneka kuthiwe ukuba unobumba w ngesiWelsh uvakaliswa ngendlela efanayo kunobumba u ngesiNgesi saseYorkshire.
Ngokwekomiti yeNdibano enoxanduva lokuqulunqa uyilo olusemthethweni lokungenisa utshintsho lwamagama: Isigqibo sokugqibela malunga nasiphi na isiqinisekiso sokubiza amalungu endibano siya kuwela ngokuqinisekileyo kumalungu ngokwawo.
UmThetho ka-2017 woRhulumente waseWales unika iNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yaseWales onke amandla okutshintsha igama layo.
NgoJuni, ikomiti yapapasha iziphumo zophando loluntu ngeziphakamiso, ngenkxaso ebanzi kwisindululo sokutshintsha igama leNdibano libe yiPalamente yaseWales.
Ngokumalunga nesihloko samalungu endlu yowiso-mthetho, nangona ikomiti yathatha Amalungu ePalamente yaseWales okanye WPM, ukhetho lweMWP lolona lufumene inkxaso ebanzi kuluntu.
Noko ke, ukuzama ukufikelela kwisivumelwano kusenokuba ngumqobo omkhulu kuSihlalo weNdlu, uElin Jones, onethemba lokuzisa isicwangciso somthetho esichaza utshintsho kwiiveki ezimbalwa.
Umthetho weenguqu uya kubandakanya ezinye iinguqu ezinxulumene nokusebenza kweNdibano, ezinje ngemithetho yokungafaneleki kwamalungu ayo kunye noyilo lwenkqubo yekomiti.
Amalungu endlu aza kwenza ivoti yokugqibela malunga negama lakhe ngexesha lengxoxo enxulumene nomthetho.
Abantu baseMacedonia baza kuvotelwa ukutshintsha igama lelizwe labo
Abemi baza kukhetha ngeCawa enoba bayafuna kusini na ukutshintsha igama lelizwe labo libe yi Republic of North Macedonia.
Le ntetho yesidlangalala yenziwa ukuze kulungiswe imbambano ekudala ikho phakathi kweGrisi nelizwe elikufutshane neGrisi, esele inommandla obizwa ngokuba yiMakedoni.
IAthens kudala igxininisa ukuba igama lommelwane wayo wasemantla libonisa indlela yokufuna umhlaba wayo kwaye iphinde yachasana nemizamo yeli lizwe yokuba yinxalenye ye-EU ne-NATO.
UMongameli waseMakedoni, uGjorge Ivanov, ongakholwayo kwindibano yesidlangalala yokutshintsha igama, uthi uza kuyijongela phantsi le voti.
Noko ke, abo baxhasa eli lungiselelo, njengoNkulumbuso uZoran Zaev, bathi ukutshintsha igama nje lixabiso lokujoyina i-EU neNATO.
Iintsimbi zeSt. Martin ziyeka ukubetha: Iingxaki zeecawa zaseHarlem
"Ngokwembali, abantu abadala endithethe nabo bathi kwakukho ibha necawa kwikona nganye", utsho njalo uMnu. Adams.
Namhlanje, akukho namnye kubo oseleyo.
Ngokutsho kukaAdams, ukunyamalala kweendawo zokutyela kunokuqondakala.
Abantu banendlela eyahlukileyo yokunxibelelana namhlanje, utsho.
Iindawo zokutyela azisafani neendawo zokuhlala ezikufutshane nalapho abantu babehlala beya khona 
Ngokuphathelele iicawa, unenkxalabo yokuba imali efunyenwe ngokuthengiswa kweeasethi ayinakuhlala ixesha elide njengoko iinkokeli zayo zicinga - kwaye kungekudala okanye kamva ziza kubuyela apho zavela khona.
Uhlabela mgama esithi, iicawa zinokuphela zithatyathelw' indawo zizakhiwo zezindlu neendawo zokuhlala ezinabantu abangenakuze bancede kwiitempile eziseleyo.
Ubuninzi babantu abathenga izindlu ezikweso sakhiwo baya kuba ngabemi abamhlophe, uthi, kwaye ngoko ke oko baya kukwenza kukuqalisa ukuvalwa kweecawa, kuba akunakwenzeka ukuba uninzi lwabantu abafudukela kwezi zakhiwo babe ngamalungu ezi cawa.
Zombini ezi cawa zakhiwa ngamabandla amhlophe ngaphambi kokuba iHarlem ibe yindawo enkulu yabantsundu; icawa ye Metropolitan Community ngo-1870 neSt. Martin's kwiminyaka elishumi kamva.
Ibandla lamaWesile elalisandul' ukubakho laphuma ngeminyaka yee-1930.
Ibandla labamnyama elalikufuphi lafumana loo sakhiwo.
ISt. Martin's yathinjwa libandla labamnyama elalikhokelwa nguMfundisi uJohn Howard Johnson, owakhokela umkhosi wokubetha abathengisi base 125th Street, enye yezona zitrato ziphambili zeHarlem, ababengafuni ukuqesha okanye ukukhuthaza abantu abamnyama.
Ngowe-1939, umlilo wabangela umonakalo omkhulu kwisakhiwo, kwaye xa amalungu ecawa kaMfundisi Johnson enza izicwangciso zokwakha kwakhona, kulapho ke apho bathumela khona inqwelo.
UMfundisi uDavid Johnson, unyana kaTata uJohnson kunye nomlandeli wakhe kwicawa yaseSt. Martin's, ngokuzingca wachaza inqwelo njenge "iintsimbi zabantu abahluphekileyo".
Ingcali eyabetha le ngxowa ngoJulayi yayichaza ngendlela eyahlukileyo: Ubutyebi benkcubeko kunye nesixhobo sembali esingenakuthelekiswa nanto.
Ingcali, uTiffany Ng weYunivesithi yaseMichigan, waphawula ukuba yayiyeyona nqwelo yokuqala edlalwa ngumculi omnyama, uDionisio A. Lind, owathi wafudukela kwivili elikhulu laseRiverside Church kwiminyaka eli-18 eyadlulayo.
NgokukaMnu. Merriweather, iSt. Martin's ayizange imthumele.
Into eye yavakala eSt. Martin's kwezi nyanga zimbalwa zidlulileyo, ngamabali entsonkothileyo abayili bezakhiwo nabenzi bezakhiwo, abanye babo benziwa ziinkokeli zecawa ezingabantu abanye benziwa yicawa yamaBhishophu.
IBhunga, elilawulayo kwiparishi, elinabalawuli abangengomaKristu, labhalela ubhishophu ngoJulayi, lichaza inkxalabo yalo yokuba ubhishophu uzama ukuhambisa iindleko kwibhunga, nangona ibhishophu yayingabandakanyekanga ekuqeshweni kwezakhiwo nabaqeshi ababethunyelwe yibhishophu.
Abanye abantu becawa baye bakhalaza ngokungabikho kokuphandle kwicawa.
Umntwana oneminyaka eli-13 ubudala wenzakala xa wayefuna iisankxwe eCalifornia
Abasemagunyeni bathi, ngoMgqibelo, kwahlaselwa kwaza kwalimala inkwenkwe eneminyaka eli-13 ubudala ngoxa yayisenza umngxuma wokufuna iisoso eCalifornia ngosuku lokuqala lonyaka wezisoso.
Ukuhlaselwa kwenzeka ngaphambi nje kwe-7 kusasa kufuphi neBeacon's Beach e-Encinitas.
Ngokutsho kukaChad Hammel kwi-KSWB-TV eSan Diego, wayechitha isiqingatha seyure enqumla kunye nabahlobo bakhe ngentsasa yangoMgqibelo xa weva ukukhala komntwana omncinane ecela uncedo.
UHammel uthi ekuqaleni wayecinga ukuba yayikukuvuya ngenxa yokubamba ihlosi, kodwa kamva wafumanisa ukuba yayikhwaza isithi 'Bandilume!
Ndilunyulwe!'
Wayenomqolo wonke oqhekekileyo, waphawula uHammel xa efika kule nkwenkwe.
"Ngenxa yokuba wonke umntu ephuma emanzini, ndakhwaza ndathi, 'Kukho umnenga emanzini!'", wongezelela watsho uHammel.
Le nkwenkwe yathunyelwa ngomoya kwisikhululo seenqwelo-moya saseRady Children's Hospital eSan Diego, apho yafakwa khona isesimeni esibi.
Akwaziwa ukuba loluphi uhlobo lomnenga olwenza oku.
Kwintlanganiso yeendaba, umhlanguli uLarry Giles wathi emva kweeveki ezimbalwa kwafunyanwa umnenga kule ndawo, kodwa kwagqitywa kwelokuba lo mnenga awungoyiki.
UGiles wongezelela wathi ixhoba lalinamanxeba okuxhuzula kwindawo ephezulu yesiphelo.
Abasemagunyeni bavala iiyure ezingama-48 ukufikelela kumanxweme ukusuka ePonto Beach eCasablad ukuya eSwami's e-Ecinitas ngenxa yophando nangeenjongo zokhuseleko.
UGiles wathi kukho iintlobo ezingaphezu kwe-135 zeeshaka kule ndawo, kodwa uninzi lwazo alugqalwa njengoluyingozi.
Izicwangciso zikaSainsbury's, kwimarike yeemveliso zobuhle yase-UK
ISainsbury's igqibe kwelokuba ikhuphisane neBoots, Superdrug kunye neDebenhams ngeendlela zokuthengisa iimveliso zobuhle ngendlela yevenkile ezinkulu ezixakekileyo ngabasebenzi abaziingcali.
Ezi ndlela zikhulu ziyinxalenye yotyalo-mali olukhulu kwimarike yeemveliso zobuhle e-UK, imarike ehamba malunga ne-2.8 yezigidigidi ze-GBP kwaye iyaqhubeka ikhula ngelixa amacandelo emfashini kunye neemveliso zasekhaya ehlala emva, kwaye iya kuvavanywa kwiivenkile ezili-11 kwilizwe liphela ukuze yandiswe kwiivenkile ezininzi kunyaka olandelayo ukuba uvavanyo luyaphumelela.
Utyalo-mali kwiimveliso zobuhle luyimveliso yokubawa kwevenkile ezinkulu ukusebenzisa indawo kwiishelufa zazo eyayisetyenziselwa umabonwakude, iimicrowave kunye neemveliso zasekhaya.
USainsbury's uthi uza kuphinda kabini umnikelo wakhe wobuhle ukuze anikeze iimveliso ezahlukeneyo ezingama-3000, kubandakanya okokuqala iimveliso ezinje ngeRevlon, Essie, Tweezerman kunye noGqirha PawPaw.
Imigca ekhoyo yeL'Oreal, iMaybelline kunye neBurt's Bees nayo iya kufumana indawo ngakumbi enendawo yeempawu ezifanayo nezo zinokufumaneka kwiivenkile ezinje ngeBhoots.
Inkampani yevenkile enkulu ikwakwisigaba sokuphinda isungule uluhlu lwayo lweemveliso zokwenza i-Boutique ukuze uninzi lweemveliso ngoku zilungele i-vegans, into efunwa ngakumbi ngabathengi abancinci.
Ivenkile ethengisa ngeempahla ethi The Fragrance Shop, iya kuvula izitolo ezimbini zeSainsbury's. Eyokuqala yenze njalo kwiveki ephelileyo eCroydon, kumazantsi eLondon, ngelixa eyesibini izakuvula eSelly Oak, eBirmingham, kamva kulo nyaka.
Ukuthenga nge-intanethi nokutshintsha kwendlela yokuthenga ukutya kwimihla ngemihla kwiivenkile ezincinane kuye kwabangela ukuba iivenkile ezinkulu zifune ezinye iindlela zokukhuthaza abantu ukuba beze.
Ngokutsho kukaMike Coupe, umphathi weSainsbury's, iivenkile ziya kufana ngakumbi neevenkile ezinkulu kumzamo wekhonkco levenkile yokutya ukulwa neevenkile ezinkulu zexabiso eliphantsi iAldi neLidl ngeenkonzo ezininzi kunye neemveliso ezingezizo zokutya.
USainsbury's uye wazisa iindawo zokuthengisa iArgos kwiivenkile zakhe ezininzi, ukongeza kwiivenkile ezininzi zaseHabitat ukusukela oko wathenga zombini ezi khonkco kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo, into athi, isebenze ukuvuselela ukuthengiswa kokutya kunye nokwandisa inzuzo yokuthenga.
Umzamo wangaphambili wale venkile yokutya wokuqalisa kwakhona amasebe ayo ezinto zobuhle kunye namayeza waphumela ekusileleni.
ISainsbury's yazama ukusebenza kunye neBoots ekuqaleni kweminyaka yoo-2000, kodwa yonke into yaphela ngokukhawuleza ngokungavumelani ngendlela yokwahlula inzuzo yenkampani yamayeza ngaphakathi kwiivenkile ezinkulu.
Esi sicwangciso sitsha siza emva kokuthengiswa kwiminyaka emithathu edlulileyo yiSainsbury's yeshishini layo lamayeza angama-281 ukuya eCelesio, umnini we-LloydsPharmacy chain, nge-GBP 125 million.
NgokukaSainsbury's, uLloyds uza kudlala indima ebalulekileyo kwisicwangciso sehlabathi, njengoko eza kwandisa uluhlu lweempawu zokunethezeka zeemveliso zolusu, ezinje ngeLa Roche-Posay okanye iVichy, ukuya kwiivenkile ezine.
UPaul Mills-Hicks, oyintloko yezorhwebo kwiSainsbury's uthi: Sitshintshe indlela ezibonakala ngayo izinto zethu zokuthambisa ukuze siphucule imeko phambi kwabathengi bethu.
Siye satyala imali kubasebenzi abaqeqeshwe ngokukhethekileyo abaya kuba luncedo kakhulu ekuboneleleni ngeengcebiso.
Uluhlu lwethu lweempawu luyilelwe ukulungelelanisa naziphi na iimfuno; kwelinye icala, imeko enomtsalane kunye nendawo esebenzayo yenza ukuba ngoku sibe yenye yeendawo ezithandwayo zeemveliso zobuhle kwaye sicela umngeni kwindlela yemveli yokuthenga.
UPeter Jones Ucaphukile emva kokuba uHolly Willoughby ehlelwe sisivumelwano se-£11 million
Inkwenkwezi ye Dragons' Den uPeter Jones wahamba ecaphukile emva kokuba umnxibelelanisi weTV uHolly Willoughby ehle emva kwesivumelwano se-GBP 11 yezigidi kunye neshishini le-brand yokuphila likaJones ukuze agxile kwiikontraki zakhe ezintsha kunye neMarks and Spencer kunye ne-ITV.
UWilloughby akanalo ixesha lokuzibandakanya kwishishini elidibeneyo leemveliso zasekhaya kunye nezixhobo zeTruly.
Ishishini lala madoda mabini eendaba lalisele lithelekiswa neGoop brand kaGwyneth Paltrow.
Umnxibelelanisi we-This Morning, oneminyaka engama-37, wasebenzisa i-Instagram ukubhengeza ukuhamba kwakhe.
UHolly Willoughby uye wenza inkwenkwezi yeDragons' Den uPeter Jones wacaphuka ngokushiya umzuzu wokugqibela kwishishini elihlangeneyo elinengeniso lemveliso yokuphila ukuze agxile kwiikontraki zakhe ezintsha kunye neMarks & Spencer neITV, eziza kumzisela inzuzo enkulu.
Ngokutsho kwemithombo eyahlukeneyo, uJones waye "enomsindo" xa inkwenkwezi yeTV ebomvu yavuma, ngexesha lentlanganiso enzima eyayibanjwe ngoLwesibini kwikomkhulu lobukhosi bakhe eMarlow, eBuckinghamshire, ukuba izivumelwano ezintsha zomnxibelelanisi, ezixabisa i-GBP 1.5 yezigidi, zibonisa ukuba akasayi kuba nexesha elaneleyo lokuzinikela kwi-truly brand yeemveliso zasekhaya kunye nezixhobo.
Ishishini laliye lafaniswa neGoop brand kaGwyneth Paltrow kwaye lalifuna ukuliphinda kabini iqashiso likaWilloughby, elixabisa i-11 yezigidi ze-GBP.
Xa uWilloughby, oneminyaka engama-37 ubudala, wasebenzisa i-Instagram ukubhengeza ukuhamba kwakhe eTruly, uJones wathatha inqwelomoya yabucala eya kwenye yeendawo zakhe zokuhlala eholide ngaphandle kwe-UK.
Ngokutsho komnye umthombo: Truly wayengumntu obalulekileyo kuHolly.
Yayimele ibe likamva lakhe elide kwaye apho sasimele simbone khona kwiminyaka engama-20 okanye engama-30 ezayo.
Isigqibo sakhe sokurhoxa sathi cwaka kuwo onke amaqela abandakanyekayo.
Akukho mntu wayekholelwayo ukuba kwenzeke ntoni ngoLwesibini, sasikufuphi kakhulu nokuqaliswa...
Kanye ngoku kukho indawo yokugcina izinto ezaliswe zizinto ezisetyenziswayo kwiziko eliphambili laseMarlow ezilungele ukuthengiswa.
Ngokutsho kweengcali, ukuhamba komethuli we This Morning, enye yeenkwenkwezi ezifumana imali eninzi e-UK, kunokubiza izigidi kwinkampani ngenxa yotyalo-mali olubalulekileyo olwenziwe kwiimveliso, ukusuka kwiipilisi nezikhanyiso ukuya kwiimpahla kunye neengubo zendlu, kunye nokwenzeka kokulibaziseka kokumiliselwa kwayo.
Ukongezelela, kusenokuthetha ukuphela kobuhlobo obude.
UWilloughby, umama wabantwana abathathu, kunye nomyeni wakhe uDan Baldwin babenobudlelwane obusondeleyo noJones kunye nomfazi wakhe uTara Capp iminyaka elishumi.
UWilloughby waseka iTruly kunye noCapp ngo-2016, kwaye uJones, oneminyaka engama-52 ubudala, wajoyina njengoSihlalo ngoMatshi.
Zombini izibini zichitha iiholide kunye. Ukongeza, uJones unamalungu angama-40% kwimveliso kamabonwakude kaBaldwin.
UWilloughby uza kuba ngunozakuzaku olandelayo lwe-M&S kwaye uza kuthatha indawo ka-Ant McPartlin njengombonisi we-ITV's I'm A Celebrity.
Umthombo osondele kuJones uthe izolo ebusuku "Asizukuphawula ngeshishini lakhe".
Izityholo ezinzima...  kwaye emva koko sathandana
Waqhula ngento yokuba uza kugxekwa ngamajelo eendaba ngokwenza into abanye abayiyolelwa ukuba "ayilunganga kumongameli" nangokuba nembono entle kangaka ngenkokeli yaseMntla Korea.
Kutheni uTrump enikezele kangaka?
UTrump wathi, ehlekisa ngelizwi lomntu obonisa iindaba:
Andizange ndinikezele nangantoni na.
Waphawula ukuba uKim wayenomdla ekubaneni intlanganiso yesibini emva kokuba eyokuqala eyayibanjelwe eSingapore ngoJuni yabhengezwa njengenyathelo elikhulu lokuchasana neNyukliya yaseMntla Korea.
Noko ke, uthethathethwano malunga nokulwa neenyukliya luye lwabambeka.
Emva kweenyanga ezingaphezu kwezintathu intlanganiso yabo ibambe eSingapore ngoJuni, umphathiswa wezopolitiko waseMntla Korea uRi Yong Ho wathi kwiinkokeli zeZizwe eziManyeneyo ngoMgqibelo ukuba uMntla Korea awuboni "impendulo ekubhaliseni" evela eMelika kwimizamo yokuqala yokulwa nezixhobo eyenziwe lilizwe lawo.
Nangona kunjalo, waphawula, i-US iyaqhubeka nokusebenzisa izohlwayo ngenjongo yokugcina uxinzelelo.
Umbono kaTrump, kwelinye icala, wawungcono kakhulu kwintetho yakhe.
"Senza kakuhle kakhulu ngeMntla Korea", watsho.
Sasiza kulwa imfazwe neNorth Korea.
Izigidi zabantu zazinokufa.
Kwaye ngoku sinalo olu lwalamano lubalaseleyo.
Ngokutsho kukaTrump, imigudu yakhe yokuphucula ubudlelwane noKim iye yavelisa iziphumo ezilungileyo: ukuphelisa uvavanyo lweentolo-mlilo, uncedo lokukhulula abathinjwa nokubuyela ekhaya kwamajoni aseMerika.
Kwaye wayikhusela indlela yakhe engaqhelekanga yokuthetha ngobudlelwane bakhe noKim.
"Kulula kakhulu ukuba ngumongameli, kodwa endaweni yokuba abantu abayi-10 000 bazame ukungena kule holo igcwele abantu, siza kuba nabantu abangama-200", watsho uTrump, ebhekisa kwisihlwele esasiphambi kwakhe.
Isiqithi esonakaliswe yinyikima nentsunami eIndonesia, kufe amakhulu abantu
Ngokomzekelo, emva kwenyikima yaseLombok, imibutho engekho phantsi kukarhulumente kwamanye amazwe yaxelelwa ukuba yayingafuneki.
Nangona abantu abangaphezu kwe-10% baseLombok kwafuneka bashiye iindawo zabo, akuzange kubhengezwe ntlekele yelizwe, nto leyo eyayifuneka ngaphambi kokuba kubekho uncedo lwamazwe ngamazwe.
Ngelishwa, kwiimeko ezininzi, baye bayenza yacaca into yokuba abaceli uncedo lwamazwe ngamazwe, ngoko ke imeko inzima, utsho uSumbung.
Nangona iSave the Children ilungiselela iqela lokuya ePalu, akukhuselekanga ukuba abantu basemzini bakwazi ukusebenza ebaleni.
Umkhulumeli we-arhente yeentlekele yaseIndonesia, uMnu. Sutopo, wathi abasemagunyeni baseIndonesia babeqwalasela imeko ePalu ukuze babone ukuba ingaba amaziko ehlabathi avunyelwe na ukuba ancedise.
Ngenxa yeenyikima ezihlala zenzeka eIndonesia, ilizwe alizange lilungele ukuhlaselwa yindalo.
Nangona iAceh iye yakha iindawo zokukhusela iitsunami, azikho rhoqo kwezinye iindawo eziselunxwemeni.
Ukungabikho kwee-siren zokulumkisa nge-tsunami ePalu, nangona kwakukho isilumkiso esisemthethweni, kusenokwenzeka ukuba kwaba negalelo kwinani labantu abafayo.
Ukuhamba phakathi kweziqithi ezininzi zaseIndonesia, kunzima gqitha.
Iintlekele zemvelo zenza kube nzima ngakumbi ukuhambisa izinto.
Inqanawa yesibhedlele eyayikwizibuko laseLombok ukuze inyamekele amaxhoba enyikima ngoku isiya ePalu; kodwa, kuya kuthatha iintsuku ezintathu ukufika kwindawo yentlekele entsha.
UMongameli Joko Widodo wayejonge ekuphuculeni iziseko zophuhliso zaseIndonesia, ibe utyale imali eninzi kwiindlela zikaloliwe neendlela ezisezantsi.
Nangona kunjalo, urhulumente kaJoko ujongene nonyaka ozayo wokuphinda anyulwe egcwele iimali.
UYoko ukwanengxaki yoxinzelelo lweqela elizimeleyo, apho amalungu amaninzi angamaSilamsi aye amkela ukholo oluthandayo.
Abantu abangaphezu kwe-1 000 ababuleweyo namashumi amawaka abafuduswe kwiindawo zabo ngenxa yokulwa kwabantu basesitratweni phakathi kwamaqela angamaKristu namaSilamsi, besebenzisa imijukujelwa, oomatolo neentolo nezinye izixhobo ezibulala abantu.
Phawula: UDaniel Sturridge waseLiverpool ubetha igowuli lokutshayisa ngombhoxo kude neChelsea
UDaniel Sturridge wasindisa iLiverpool kwilahleko kwiPremier League kwiChelsea ngegowuli lakhe elibhalwe ngomzuzu wama-89 ngoMgqibelo eStamford Bridge, eLondon.
USturridge wafumana ukudlula kukaXherdan Shaqiri malunga ne-27 yeemitha ukusuka kwicala le-Chelsea xa iqela lakhe lalihamba lilahlekelwa yi-1-0.
Wayibeka ibhola ngasekhohlo ngaphambi kokuba adlale ibhola ekhethekileyo kwibhola yesibini.
Umpu wawugqitha wonke ummandla ngokuphakama okukhulu njengoko wawusondela kwiqhina lasekunene lomgcini wegosa.
Ibhola ekugqibeleni yaqalisa ukwehla phezu kweKepa Arrizabalaga egxalathelana ukuzama ukuyithintela yaza yaphela emazantsi enethi.
Ndandidla ngokuzama ukufikelela kuloo ndawo ukuze ndikwazi ukudubula, kwaye abadlali abanjengoShaqiri bahlala bedlala phambili kangangoko kunokwenzeka, ngoko ndazama ukuzenzela ixesha elininzi kangangoko kunokwenzeka, utshilo uSturridge kwiLiverpoolFC.com.
