IChelsea yayiphumelela ngo-1-0 ngexesha lokuphumla emva kokubetha igowuli ngomzuzu wama-25 ngenkwenkwezi yayo yaseBelgium uEden Hazard.
Kwidlala, umqhubi weqela leBlue wabuyisela inqindi enye kuMateo Kovacic ngaphambi kokuba aqalise phantse embindini wenkundla aze aqhubele phambili ukuya ebaleni laseLiverpool.
UKovacic wenza umdibaniso okhawulezayo ukusuka embindini wenkundla.
Emva koko, wenza ukudlula okukhulu nzulu, okwashiya uHazard ngaphakathi kwindawo enebhola elawulwayo.
UHazard wayigqitha ukhuseleko ukuze aphelelise kwipali yesibini ngepiki ngomlenze wasekhohlo apho umgcini wegosa waseLiverpool uAlisson Becker akazange afike khona.
ILiverpool iza kudibana neNaples kwisigaba seqela leChampions League ngoLwesithathu olandelayo ngentsimbi yesi-3:00 eStadio San Paolo eNaples, eItali.
I-Chelsea, yona, iya kudlala ne-VideoTon kwi-UEFA Europa League ngoLwesine ngo-15:00 eLondon.
