Amapolisa abamba indoda eneminyaka engama-32 ubudala ekrokrelwa ukuba ibulele emva kokufumana ibhinqa libethelelwe
Uphando ngokubulala luqale emva kokuba umzimba womfazi ufunyenwe ngale ntsasa eBirkenhead, eMerseyside.
Ibhinqa, elineminyaka engama-44 ubudala, lafunyanwa ngeye-7:55 nge-pickets ezininzi eGrayson Mews, John Street; emva koko, indoda eneminyaka engama-32 ubudala yabanjwa njengomntu okrokrelwa ukubulala.
Amapolisa ayalela ukuba abantu abahlala kuloo ndawo ababona okanye beva into enxulumene nolu lwaphulo-mthetho babhenele kumagosa karhulumente.
Ngokutsho komhloli uBrian O'Hagan: Nangona uphando lusemgangathweni wokuqala, ndifuna ukubiza nabani na osondele kuJohn Street eBirkenhead nowayenokubona okanye eve nantoni na ekrokrisayo, ukuba acele ukunxibelelana nathi.
Ndingathanda ukubiza nabani na, ngakumbi abaqhubi beeteksi abakhe bafumana nantoni na ngekhamera yenqwelo-mafutha, ukuba banxibelelane, kuba banokuba nolwazi olubalulekileyo kuphando.
Isithethi samapolisa siqinisekisile ukuba lo mfazi uswelekileyo usuka eBirkenhead yaye wafunyanwa ngaphakathi kwindlu.
Ngengokuhlwa, abahlobo abacinga ukuba bayazi le nkosikazi baye bafika kwindawo yolwaphulo-mthetho ukubuza imibuzo malunga nendawo awafunyanwa kuyo ngale ntsasa.
Ngoxa uphando luqhubeka, amapolisa athi ayazisa izalamane ezisondeleyo zexhoba.
Umqhubi weteksi ohlala eGrayson Mews usandul' ukuzama ukubuyela kwigumbi lakhe, kodwa amapolisa athi akukho mntu uvumelekileyo ukuba angene okanye aphume kweso sakhiwo.
Wathi akuva oko kwenzekileyo, akakwazi ukuthetha.
Abahlali bayaxelelwa ukuba kuza kuthatha iiyure ngaphambi kokuba bakwazi ukungena.
Kwakunokuviwa igosa lasebupoliseni lixelela enye indoda ukuba le ndawo iphela yayiphathwa njengendawo yokwenzakala.
Umfazi wabonakala kwindawo yesiganeko ekhala.
