Umfanekiso oqingqiweyo kaCromwell wePalamente yaseBritane uba sisikhumbuzo sokugqibela esichaphazelekayo kwingxoxo malunga Ukubhala kwakhona imbali
Ukutshatyalaliswa kwakhe kwakuza kuba luhlobo oluthile lobulungisa bokubonisa indlela amaTaliban ayitshabalalisa ngayo izinto ezininzi zenkcubeko nezonqulo eNgilani ngabalandeli bawo ababenenzondelelo.
Nangona kunjalo, iCromwell Society ichaze isindululo sikaCrick njenge "buvuvu" kunye "nomzamo wokubhala kwakhona imbali".
UJohn Goldsmith, umongameli weCromwell Society, uthi: Kwingxoxo yangoku malunga nokususwa kwemifanekiso eqingqiweyo, kwakungenakuphepheka ukuba umfanekiso ka-Oliver Cromwell phambi kwebhotwe laseWestminster uza kuba yinjongo ephambili.
I-iconoclasm yeemfazwe zasekuhlaleni zaseNgilani ayizange ilawulwe okanye iqhutywe nguCromwell.
Mhlawumbi wayeza kugqiba ngokubulala uCromwell ongalunganga ngenxa yezenzo zokhokho bakhe ezenziwa ngenkulungwane edlulileyo.
Ukumelwa kukaCromwell nguSir William Hamo Thorneycroft kububungqina benkolelo yenkulungwane ye-19 yaye yinxalenye yembali yomntu abaninzi abasakholelwa ukuba ufanele ukukhunjulwa.
UGoldsmith wathi kwiThe Sunday Telegraph: UCromwell uthathwa ngabaninzi, mhlawumbi ngasekupheleni kwenkulungwane ye-19 kunokuba kunjalo ngoku, njengomkhuseli wepalamente phambi koxinzelelo lwangaphandle, kwimeko yakhe ngokucacileyo ubukumkani.
Ukuba le nto ingumboniso ochanekileyo okanye hayi ihlala iyingxoxo yembali.
Into eyinyani kukuba ingxabano yasembindini wenkulungwane ye-17 yabumba uphuhliso olulandelayo lwesizwe sethu, yaye uCromwell ngumntu owaziwayo omela icala elinye laloo mbambano.
Iimpumelelo zakhe njengoMkhuseli oyiNkosi nazo zifanelwe kukubhiyozelwa nokukhunjulwa.
Ingulube Ebulalayo Ibulala Umfama WaseTshayina
Umfama uhlaselwe waza wabulawa yingulube kwimarike ekumzantsi-ntshona weChina, ngokutsho kwemithombo yasekuhlaleni.
Le ndoda, ekwaziwa ngegama layo lokugqibela elithi Yuan, yafunyanwa ifile inethambo lomgudu, igutyungelwe ligazi kufuphi nebala lehagu kwimarike yaseLiupanshui kwiphondo laseGuizhou, ingxelo yeSouth China Morning Post yathi ngeCawa.
NgoMeyi 30, 2005, umfuyi weehagu wayelungiselela ukujova izitofu kwihagu kwiyadi eXining, kwiPhondo laseQinghai, eChina.
Kuyaziwa ukuba, ngoLwesithathu wayehambe nomza wakhe besuka kwiphondo elingummelwane laseYunnan besiya kuthengisa iihagu ezili-15 emarikeni.
Ngentsasa elandelayo, umzala wakhe wamfumana efile waza wafumanisa ucango oluvulekileyo olwalukhangele kwihlathi lehagu eliselumelwaneni.
Wathi, enkundleni kwakukho ingulube enkulu eyindoda enegazi emlonyeni wayo.
Uphando lwezamayeza lwangqina ukuba umfama wayethwaliswe inxeba elibuhlungu ngumthi onobunzima obuziikhilogram ezingama-250, ngokwengxelo.
Umzala wam wayenemilenze eyaphukileyo nezele ligazi, watsho umzala wakhe, ogama linguWu, ngokutsho kweendaba zangokuhlwa zaseGuyang.
Iifoto ezirekhodiweyo zekhamera zibonisa uYuan engena kwimarike ngentsimbi ye-4:40 kusasa ngoLwesine ukuze ondle iihagu.
Umzimba wakhe wafunyanwa malunga neyure kamva.
Isilwanyana esabulala loo mntu sasingengowakwaYuan okanye umza wakhe.
Omnye umongameli wentengiso wathi kwiindaba zangokuhlwa ukuba ingulube yahlala ivaliwe kwaye yahlukaniswa ukuze ithintele ukuba ingahlaseli nabani na omnye, ngelixa amapolisa eqokelela ubungqina kwindawo yolwaphulo-mthetho.
Kuxelwe ukuba intsapho kaYuan kunye namagosa emarike athetha-thethana ngomonakalo obangelwe kukufa kwakhe.
Nangona zingaqhelekanga, kukho iimeko zangaphambili zehagu ezihlasela abantu.
Ngowe-2016, ingulube yahlasela umfazi nomyeni wakhe kwifama yabo eMassachusetts, yaza yamshiya enamanxeba amakhulu.
Kwiminyaka elishumi eyadlulayo, ingulube enobunzima obuziikhilogram ezingama-300 yabamba umfama waseWales yaze yabetha itrektara yakhe de umfazi wayo wakwazi ukuyityhafisa.
Emva kokuba umfama wase-Oregon edliwe ziihagu zakhe ngo-2012, umfama waseManitoba uxelele i-CBC News ukuba iihagu azisoloko zinobundlobongela kodwa incasa yegazi inokusebenza njenge "trigger".
