Iintsalela zeNkanyamba uRosa ziza kuzisa izantyalantyala zemvula kulo lonke elaseMzantsi-ntshona Merika
Ngokutsho kweenkcukacha, iNkanyamba uRosa iya isiba buthathaka njengoko ihamba phezu kwamanzi abandayo kunxweme olusemantla eMexico.
Noko ke, iRosa iza kuzisa imvula enkulu kulo lonke elaseMexico ekumntla nakwimpuma-ntshona yeUnited States kwiintsuku ezizayo.
I-Rosa yayinezivunguvungu eziziikhilomitha ezili-138 ngeyure, eziqhelekileyo kwiNkanyamba yeCandelo 1, ngentsimbi yesi-5 ekuseni ngeCawa, ixesha laseMpuma ye-US, kwaye yabekwa kwiikhilomitha ezingama-620 kumazantsi-ntshona ePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
Kulindeleke ukuba iRosa iye emantla ngeCawa.
Ngelo xesha, uqalisa ukuvela njengodandatheko kuLwandlekazi lwePasifiki, oluya ngasempuma ukuya kunxweme olusentshona lwe-US. Xa uRosa esondela kwi-Baja California Peninsula ngoMvulo njengesiphepho esishushu, uya kuqala ukushiya umswakama omkhulu osempuma ukuya emantla ukuya kumazantsi mpuma e-US.
I-Rosa iza kushiya imvula efikelela kwi-250 mm kwezinye iindawo eMexico ngoMvulo.
Emva koko, umswakama weqhwa uya kusebenzisana nokuxinezeleka okusondelayo ukuvelisa imvula enkulu ngokubanzi kuwo wonke umzantsi-ntshona kwiintsuku ezizayo.
Kwiindawo ezininzi, i-25 ukuya kwi-100 mm yemvula iza kubangela imisinga eyingozi, imisinga yenkunkuma kunye nokwenzeka kokuchithwa komhlaba entlango.
Umswakama omkhulu weTropiki uza kubangela imvula emalunga nama-50 ukuya kuma-75 mm ngeyure kwiindawo ezahlukeneyo, ngakumbi kwiindawo ezisemazantsi eNevada naseArizona.
Kulindeleke i-50 ukuya kwi-100 mm yemvula kwiindawo ezisemazantsi mpuma, ngakumbi kwindawo enkulu yaseArizona.
Kukho ithuba lokuba kuvele imilambo, ekubeni imeko isiba mandundu ngokukhawuleza ngenxa yemvula yeetropiki.
Akucetyiswa ngokupheleleyo ukungena entlango ngeenyawo ngenxa yesisongelo semvula yetropiki.
Izantyalantyala zemvula zinokubangela ukuba imijelo ibe yimilambo engalawulwayo, yaye izaqhwithi zinokuzisa imimoya enamandla namafu othuli kwiindawo ezithile.
Le ngxaki iza kuzisa izantyalantyala zemvula kwiindawo ezithile kunxweme lwaseMzantsi California.
Kunokwenzeka ukuba kubhalwe inani elipheleleyo lemvula elingaphezulu kwe-50 mm, elinokubangela ukuhamba kwenkunkuma encinci kunye neendlela ezinamatye.
Oku kuya kuba yimvula yokuqala yexesha lemvula kulo mmandla.
Kuya kuqala ukufika iziqwenga zemvula ezikhanyayo zaseArizona phakathi kobusuku beCawa nentsasa yangoMvulo, ngaphambi kokuba imvula ibe yinto eqhelekileyo phakathi kobusuku bangoMvulo nangoLwesibini.
Imvula eninzi iza kunetha kummandla weZine Corners ngoLwesibini ize iqhubeke ngoLwesithathu.
Ngo-Oktobha kuza kubakho amaqondo obushushu amaninzi kulo lonke elaseUnited States njengoko iArctic iphola, nangona amazwekazi asezantsi aya kuhlala eshushu.
Le nto inokubangela ngamanye amaxesha utshintsho olukhulu lobushushu kumgama omfutshane.
Ummandla ophakathi weUnited States ngeCawa ngumzekelo ocacileyo womahluko obonakalayo wobushushu.
Kukho umahluko wobushushu obuphantse bube ngama-20 degrees phakathi kweKansas City, eMissouri, neOmaha, eNebraska, naphakathi kweSt. Louis neDes Moines, eIowa.
Kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo, ubushushu basehlotyeni buya kuzama ukwanda kwakhona.
Kulindeleke ukuba iqale ngo-Oktobha ishushu kwiindawo ezininzi ezikwindawo ekumbindi nasempuma ye-US, ngamaqondo obushushu ajikeleze ama-27 degrees ukusuka kwindawo yaseMazantsi ukuya kwiindawo ezikwimpuma mpuma.
Isixeko saseNew York sinokufikelela kuma-27 degrees ngoLwesibini, nto leyo enokubonisa malunga nama-10 degrees ngaphezulu komndilili.
Ngokutsho kwengxelo yemozulu yexesha elide, kukho amathuba amaninzi okuba kuvele amaqondo obushushu angaphezulu komyinge kwimpuma yeUnited States kwisiqingatha sokuqala sikaOktobha.
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele ingxelo kaBrett Kavanaugh
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele ubungqina obushukumisayo obunikelwa ngumgqatswa weNkundla Ephakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh nomfazi owayemtyhola ngokuxhaphaza ngokwesondo, ekuthiwa kwenzeka kwiminyaka yee-1980, uChristine Blasey Ford.
Okwangoku, ukuphazamiseka kwezopolitiko kuyaqhubeka, njengoko amajelo osasazo etshintsha ucwangciso lwawo lwangoLwesihlanu ngenxa yenguqu yemini yokugqibela: isivumelwano esenziwe nguSenator waseArizona uJeff Flake sokuba iFBI iphando ngamatyala kangangeveki.
UFord wachazela iKomiti yeNkundla yeSenate ukuba wayeqinisekile ukuba uKavanaugh wamchukumisa enxilile waza wazama ukumkhulula iimpahla zakhe kwitheko lasesikolweni.
UKavanaugh, kwiingxelo zakhe ezikhuthazayo, wathi wayeqinisekile ukuba oku akuzange kwenzeke.
Ngokutsho kukaNielsen, kusenokwenzeka ukuba abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20.4 babukele le vidiyo ngoLwesihlanu.
Le nkampani yayibalwa umndilili wababukeli bezitishi zeCBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kunye neMSNBC.
Amanani ababukeli ayengekho ngokukhawuleza kwezinye iinkonzo ezazisazisa ubungqina, ezinje ngePBS, C-SPAN okanye iFox Business Network.
Kwakhona, uNelsen udla ngokuba neengxaki ekubaleni abantu ababukelayo kwiofisi yakhe.
Xa sijonga izinto ngendlela efanelekileyo, abantu ababukeleyo bafana nabantu ababukele umdlalo webhola ekhatywayo okanye ababukele umsitho weOscar.
I-Fox News Channel, iinkokeli zengcamango eziye zaxhasa ngokucacileyo ukuqeshwa kukaKavanaugh, yayiyeyona nethwekhi inabantu abaninzi, kunye nomlinganiselo wababukeli abazizigidi ezi-5,69 ngexesha lobungqina bemini yonke, ngokutsho kukaNielsen.
I-ABC yayisesibini nge-3.26 yezigidi zababukeli.
I-CBS yafumana i-3.1 yezigidi, i-NBC i-2.94 yezigidi, i-MSNBC i-2.89 yezigidi kunye ne-CNN i-2.52 yezigidi, ngokweenkcukacha zikaNielsen.
