Inkulumbuso yaseBritani uMay utyhola abagxeki bakhe ngokudlala ngezopolitiko malunga neBrexit
Inkulumbuso uTheresa May utyhola abagxeki becebo lakhe lokushiya i-European Union "ngokudlala ngezopolitiko" ngekamva le-UK nangokungahoyi umdla wesizwe kudliwano-ndlebe nephephandaba iSunday Times.
Inkulumbuso yaseBritani uTheresa May ufika kwinkomfa yeqela leTherapy eBirmingham, e-United Kingdom, nge-29 kaSeptemba 2018.
Kwinto enye edliwanondlebe noMay kwiphepha lokuqala, owayesakuba nguMphathiswa wezeMicimbi yeZangaphandle kaMay uBoris Johnson waqinisa ukuhlasela kwakhe oko kubizwa ngokuba sisicwangciso seChequers seBrexit, apho athi isindululo sokuba i-UK ne-EU bahlawule irhafu omnye komnye asiyonto .
