Abasemagunyeni bakhupha ividiyo yomlo phakathi kukaSims noSimpson.
Amapolisa afumana ezi zibuko kwindawo yolwaphulo-mthetho kwaye athi afumene iDNA kaSimpson kuzo, ngokutsho kwe-CBS affiliate WAFB.
Emva kokudlan' indlebe noSimpson, lo wavuma ukuba wadubula uWayde, ngokutsho kwamapolisa.
Ibheyile yakhe ibekwe kwi-350 000 USD, ngokutsho kommeli.
I-ofisi ye-coroner yase-East Baton Rouge yakhupha ingxelo yokuqala ngoLwesihlanu, ithi unobangela wokufa yayikukubulawa ngesibhamu entloko entanyeni.
ISebe libulela iQela Elilawulayo Leembacu laseLouisiana, iLebhu Yolwaphulo-mthetho yaseLouisiana, iSouthern University Police nelali ngokuxhasa uphando oluye lwaphumela kulo mntu ubanjiweyo.
UMlawuli wezemidlalo weLSU uJoe Alleva wavakalisa umbulelo wakhe kumagosa omthetho wengingqi ngenxa "yokukhuthala kwawo nokufuna ubulungisa".
USims wayeneminyaka engama-20 ubudala.
Umyinge we-1.98 m, wadlala kwiphiko kwaye wakhulela eBaton Rouge, apho uyise, uWayne, naye wayengumdlali webhasikithi kwiqela le-LSU.
Wafumana amanqaku angama-5.6 kunye nama-2.6 okuphakamisa ukuqala kwisizini ephelileyo.
Ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu, umqeqeshi webhasikithi weLSU uWill Wade wathi iqela "libhidekile" kwaye ukufa kukaWayde "kwakunzima kakhulu".
