Intaba-mlilo ekhupha umlotha kwisiXeko saseMexico
Umlotha owavutha kwintaba-mlilo iPopocatepetl uye wafikelela kwimimandla ekumzantsi weMexico City.
Iziko lelizwe lokuthintela iintlekele ngoMgqibelo lixelele abantu baseMexico ukuba bahlale kude nentaba-mlilo emva kokuba kufunyenwe umsebenzi entabeni yaye kwaphuma iigesi nomlotha ezili-183 kwisithuba seeyure ezingama-24.
Eli ziko lalijonge iintlantsi ezininzi neenyikima ezazisandul' ukwenzeka.
Iifoto ezikwiintanethi zentlalo zibonisa abantu bebona uthuthu olucekeceke kwiivili zeemoto kwiidolophu zaseMexico ezifana neXochimilco.
Izazi ngeenkwenkwezi zithe zafumanisa ukuba le ntaba-mlilo ikumgama oziikhilomitha eziyi-72 kumazantsi mpuma esixeko ukususela oko inyikima enkulu enobungakanani be-7.1 yahlasela kumbindi weMexico ngoSeptemba 2017.
Intaba-mlilo, eyaziwa ngokuba yi-Don Goyo, iye yahlala isebenza ukususela ngo-1994.
Amapolisa axabana nabazimeleyo baseCatalan ngaphambi nje komhla wokuzalwa kwendibano yesigqibo sokuzimela
Abantu abathandathu babanjwa eBarcelona ngoMgqibelo emva kokuba abaqhankqalazi abaxhasa ukuzimela beqhankqalaze namapolisa, yaye amawaka abantu abambelela kwimiboniso yokuqhankqalaza yokukhumbula isikhumbuzo sokuqala sokuvota kweCatalonia.
Iqela labantu abazimeleyo ababanjwe ngamapolisa abakhuselayo baqalisa ukuwaphosa amaqanda kunye nepeyinti eluthuli, nto leyo eyabangela ukuba kuvele amafu amnyama othuli kwizitrato eziqhelekileyo ezizele ngabakhenkethi.
Kamva ngaloo mini, kwabakho ukuxabana namapolisa, awasebenzisa izibonda zawo ukuze athintele abaqhankqalazi abanogonyamelo.
Kangangeeyure eziliqela, amaqela azimeleyo ayecula esithi Asizakulibala, asixoleli ubuso ngobuso nabaqhankqalazi abamanyeneyo ababethi Phila ixesha elide eSpeyin.
Abantu abali-14 kwafuneka banyangwe ngenxa yokwenzakala kancinane ngexesha loqhankqalazo, ngokutsho kwemithombo yasekuhlaleni.
Uxinzelelo aluzange luncitshiswe kulo mmandla unembono yokuzimela ngonyaka emva kokuba ngo-Oktobha 1 kwaqhutywa intetho yesigqibo eyayigqalwa njengephosakeleyo yiMadrid kodwa yayisenziwa ngabaqhawuli bamaCatalan.
Abavoti bakhetha ukuzimela ngobuninzi, nangona inqanaba lokuthatha inxaxheba laliphantsi, kuba abo bachasene nokuzimela ngokuzimeleyo bawuqhankqalaza ubukhulu becala.
Ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni baseCatalan, phantse abantu abayi-1 000 bonzakele kunyaka ophelileyo emva kokuba amapolisa ezame ukuphazamisa ukuvota ngokungena kwiindawo zokuvota kulo lonke eli phondo, nto leyo eyabangela uqhushululu.
Amaqela azimelayo azalela ubusuku bonke ngoLwesihlanu ukuze aphephe umngcelele owawuza kubonisa inkxaso kumapolisa asekuhlaleni.
Lo mboniso wawusenzeka, kodwa abaqhankqalazi banyanzeleka ukuba bathathe olunye uhambo.
UNarcís Termes, umbane oneminyaka engama-68 ubudala nomnye wabathathi-nxaxheba kumboniso wokuzimela kunye nomfazi wakhe, wathi akasenazo ithemba lokuba iCatalonia ingazizimela.
Unyaka ophelileyo waba ngomnye wamaxesha amnandi.
Ndabona abazali bam belila ngenxa yovuyo lokuba bakwazi ukuvota, kodwa ngoku siziva singenakuzenzela nto, utshilo.
Nangona iphumelele kakhulu, nangona iphantse yaphumelela, kunyulo lwaseburhulumenteni olwenzeka ngoDisemba, amaqela azimeleyo aseCatalan aye azibona sele enengxaki yokugcina amandla kulo nyaka, njengoko iinkokeli zawo ezininzi zikwindawo yokuzihlalisa okanye zisavalelwe zilinde ukuxoxwa kwetyala ngenxa yendima yazo ekuququzeleleni intetho yesigqibo kunye nokuvakaliswa kwenkululeko.
UJoan Puig, owenza oomatshini oneminyaka engama-42 ubudala, ubhala phantsi umboniso wokuxhasa amapolisa ngomnxeba wakhe, kwaye uthi ingxabano ivuselelwe ziipolitiki kumacala omabini.
Uxinezeleko luyanda, utsho.
NgoMgqibelo, uOriol Junqueras, omnye wabalawuli abasithoba baseCatalan abavalelwe entolongweni ngaphambi kokuba bagwetywe ukususela ekupheleni konyaka ophelileyo, wabhengeza ukuba uza kulwela ukhetho lwePalamente yaseYurophu kunyaka ozayo.
Ukuzimisa njengonyulo kunyulo lwaseYurophu yeyona ndlela yokuchaza ukubuyela emva kwamanani entando yesininzi kunye noxinzelelo esilubonileyo kurhulumente waseSpain, uthi.
ILondonderry: Amadoda abanjwe emva kokutyala imali kwindlu enemoto
Amadoda amathathu aneminyaka engama-33, 34 nama-39 ubudala abanjwe emva kokuba imoto ibethe indlu yaseLondonderry.
Le ngxaki yenzeke eBallynagard Crescent ngoLwesine malunga ne-19:30 yure ngexesha lendawo.
UMhloli Bob Blemmings uthi kwenzeke umonakalo kwiingcango nakwisakhiwo ngokwaso.
Kusenokwenzeka ukuba, ngaxa lithile, umntu othile wakhupha umpu waza wadubaduba imoto.
Umdlalo kaMenga ubangela ukuba iLivingston iphumelele ngo-1-0 kwiRangers
Injongo yokuqala kaDolly Menga neLivingston yaba yimpumelelo
U-Livingston, owayenyuke kulo nyaka, wamangalisa i-Glasgow Rangers kwinto nje eyisehlulelo sesibini sikaSteven Gerrard kwimidlalo eli-18 njengomqeqeshi weklabhu yase-Ibrox.
Umdlalo kaDolly Menga wenza umahluko, kuba, ngolu loyiso, iqela likaGary Holt linyuka liye kwindawo yesibini, eliya kubelana ngayo neHibernian.
Iqela likaGerrard, kwelinye icala, liqhubeka lingaphumelelanga ekhaya kwiPremiership kule sizini. NgeCawa ezayo liza kudibana nenkokeli, iHearts, elidityaniswe yimbambano yamanqaku asibhozo.
Kodwa ngaphambi koko, iRangers iya kwamkela iVienna Rapid kweli ngoLwesine kwi Europa League.
I-Livingston, okwangoku, yandisa ukuya kwimidlalo emithandathu umjikelo wayo ongenasiphelo kwiligi, kunye noHolt njengomqeqeshi ongasazi ukuba yintoni ukulahleka okoko wathatha indawo kaKenny Miler kwinyanga ephelileyo.
I-Livingston ayizisebenzisi amathuba ayo phambi komdlalo othe ngqo weendwendwe
Iqela likaHolt bekufanele ukuba liye phambili kwinqwelo-mafutha ngaphambi kokuba lifumane inqaku, kuba umdlalo walo othe ngqo wabangela zonke iintlobo zeengxaki kwiRangers.
UScott Robinson wavula indlela yakhe phakathi kukhuselo kodwa waphulukana nethuba lakhe xa wayephambi komgcini wegosa. Emva koko, uAlan Lithgow wathumela ibhola ngaphandle ehlala phantsi ezama ukugqiba intloko kaCraig Halkett, owela umgcini wegosa.
Abantu basekuhlaleni babesele bekhululekile ukuvumela iRangers ukuba isondele kwindawo yabo, kuba babesazi ukuba banokubangela iingxaki kwiindwendwe kumdlalo wodwa.
Kwaye yiloo nto le nto yabangela ukuba kubethwe igowuli.
Umphathi wabetha ityala ngokuchasene neminqweno yeRangers kwaye u-Livingston wenza ukuvulwa kwibhanti, apho u-Declan Gallagher noRobinson badibanisa ukuze uMenga akwazi ukubetha kuqala aze aphelelise ukusuka embindini wendawo.
Ngelo xesha, iRangers yayilawula ubuncwane, kodwa yafumana ukhuseleko olungaphaya kunye nomgcini wegosa uLiam Kelly owayenomsebenzi omncinci kakhulu kulo mdlalo,
Lo mfanekiso waphinda wavela kwinxalenye yesibini, nangona uAlfredo Morelos wanyanzela uKelly ukuba enze umlo wokuqhawula.
Kwelinye icala, umgcini wegosa waseRangers uAllan McGregor wamisa ngeenyawo ithuba likaScott Pittman waza uLithgow wagqiba ekhokelela kwelinye iqhosha elidibeneyo likaLivingston.
I-Rangers yazinikela ekuxhonyeni enye enye iibhola kwindawo yaseLivingston, kuphela ukuba zilahlwe. Ukongeza, kwafunwa izohlwayo ezimbini, enye ngokungeniswa kukaHalkett kwindawo yokutshintsha uGlenn Middleton, kunye nenye ngezandla. Zombini zalahlwa.
Livingston  phenomenal: uhlalutyo
U-Alasdair Lamont we-BBC eScotland kwi-Tony Macaroni Arena
Wenze kakuhle kakhulu uLivingston.
Indoda ithi babebalasele, yaye bayaqhubeka begqwesa zonke izinto ebezibekelwe phambi kwabo.
Indlela yakhe yokudlala kunye nabasebenzi bakhe abaguqukanga kangako ukusukela ekubuyeni kwakhe kwinqanaba eliphezulu, nangona uninzi lwemfanelo kufuneka inikwe uHolt ngendlela athe wayibeka ngayo iqela ukusukela oko wafika.
Kwakukho iqela elikhulu lamaqhawe.
UKaputeni Halkett waye mkhulu, ekhokela ukhuselo olwalulungiselelwe ngokugqibeleleyo, ngelixa uConnor Goldson noJoe Worrall kwafuneka bexhonywe nguMenga kulo lonke umdlalo.
I-Rangers yayingasenazo izizathu zokukhuthaza, nangona kunjalo.
Nangona kukho amaxesha amnandi kunye noGerrard njengomqeqeshi, ngokuqinisekileyo abakwazi ukugcina umgangatho.
Abazange bakwazi ukudala amathuba (kuphela kanye baphumelela ngokucacileyo ukhuseleko lwasekhaya), kwaye oku iRangers, esecaleni eliphakathi kwetafile, kufuneka ithathwe njengesilumkiso.
