Yonke into yayimomotheka kwaye isibhakabhaka siqaqambile ngoMgqibelo (Septemba 29) xa iinkokeli zaseTurkey naseJamani zahlanganisana eBerlin ukuze zitye isidlo sakusasa.
Yayilusuku lokuqala lotyelelo olwaluphikisana lukaMongameli Erdogan eJamani, olwalunomdla wokulungisa ubudlelwane phakathi kwamazwe amabini angamalungu eNATO.
