Zombini ezi ziganeko zibonisa indlela abahluke ngayo abantu ababekunye naye, abanye bejonga lo mntu njengegorha, abanye bembiza ngokuba ngumlawuli.
Ingozi yemoto yaseDepford: umgibeli webhayisekile usweleka emva kokubethwa yimoto
