Le ngozi yenzeka kwiinyanga ezimbalwa emva kokuba omnye umkhweli webhayisekile eswelekile kwingozi yokugqogqa abaleka eChilders Street, kumgama weekhilomitha ezi-1.6 ukusuka kwindawo yengozi yangoMgqibelo.
