Abasebenzi abathandathu baye banyangwa ngenxa yokwenzakala.
Asiluvumeli ugonyamelo ezintolongweni zethu, yaye siyaqonda ukuba abo babangela le ngxabano baza kuphendula emapoliseni yaye basenokuvalelwa ixesha elide.
KwiNtolongo yaseLong Lartin kukho amabanjwa angaphezu kwama-500, kuquka ezinye zezona mpula-mthetho ziyingozi.
NgoJuni, kwafunyaniswa ukuba umphathi wentolongo kwafuneka ayalelwe esibhedlele emva kokuba ehlasele elinye ibanjwa.
Ukongezelela, ngo-Oktobha wonyaka ophelileyo, amagosa okulwa nobutyebi aye afika entolongweni ukuze aphelise ingxabano enkulu apho abasebenzi basejele bahlaselwa ngeebhola zebhiliya.
INkanyamba uRosa isongela iPhoenix, eLas Vegas naseSalt Lake City ngamanzi amakhulu (imimandla enesomiso inokuxhamla)
Akuqhelekanga ukuba inkanyamba ihlasele iArizona, kodwa oku koko kusenokwenzeka ekuqaleni kweveki ezayo xa oko kuseleyo kweNkanyamba uRosa kudlula entlango ekumzantsi-ntshona, kunobungozi bokutshona kwamanzi.
I-National Weather Service sele ikhuphe izilumkiso zenkanyamba ngoMvulo nangoLwesibini kwintshona yeArizona ukuya kumazantsi nasempuma yeNevada, kumazantsi mpuma eCalifornia naseUtah, kuquka izixeko zasePhoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas naseSalt Lake City.
Kulindeleke ukuba u-Rosa afike ngqo ePhoenix ngoLwesibini aze aqhubeke nemvula ngoMvulo ebusuku.
I-Phoenix National Weather Service yathi kwiphephancwadi layo lephephancwadi, ziinkanyamba ezilishumi elinesibini kuphela eziye zahlala zikwiqhwa okanye zikhuselekile kwindawo engangeekhilomitha ezingama-322 ukusuka ePhoenix ukususela ngowe-1950.
INkanyamba uKatrina (1967) yahlala kwiikhilomitha ezingama-64 ukusuka kumda waseArizona.
Iimodeli zakutshanje zeziko lesizwe leenkanyamba ziqikelela i-50 ukuya kwi-100 mm yemvula, eneendawo ezizimeleyo apho kuya kubhaliswa ukuya kuthi ga kwi-150 mm eMogollon yaseArizona.
Ezinye iindawo ezikwintlango ekumzantsi-ntshona, kuquka iCentral Rockies neGreat Basin, zinokubhala i-25 ukuya kwi-50 mm, kunye nethuba leendawo ezizimeleyo ukuya kuthi ga kwi-100 mm.
Kwiindawo ezingasengozini yokukhukula, imvula yaseRosa inokuba ziindaba ezimnandi kuba lo mmandla uneembalela.
Nangona imvula ininzi, inokuba luncedo kuba ummandla osemazantsi-ntshona unxunguphele.
Ngokutsho kweU.S. Drought Control, ngaphezu kwama-40 ekhulwini eArizona anengxaki yobushushu obukhulu, obona buninzi, ngokutsho kweweather.com.
Kodwa kuqala, iNkanyamba uRosa iza kufika kwicala elingaselunxwemeni lwaseBaja California, eMexico.
I-Rosa yaqhubeka inamandla njengesaqhwithi ngeCawa kusasa, inomoya omkhulu we-137 km/h, kwaye ngoku ikumgama we-620 km kumzantsi wePunta Eugenia, eMexico, ihamba ngasentla ngesantya se-20 km/h.
Eli saqhwithi lifumana amanzi abandayo kwiPasifiki, nto leyo eyenza ukuba liphelelwe ngamandla.
Ngoko ke, kulindeleke ukuba ifike eMexico njengesaqhwithi esinamandla ngoMvulo emva kwemini okanye ngokuhlwa.
Imvula eninzi inokuwa kwiindawo ezahlukeneyo zaseMexico, ibe kusenokubakho imvula enkulu.
Ngokwe weather.com, kulindeleke i-75 ukuya kwi-150 mm iyonke yemvula ukusuka eBaja California ukuya kumantla ntshona eSonora, kunye nethuba lokufikelela kwi-250 mm.
Emva koko, iRosa iya kuya emantla inqumla iMexico ngamandla esitshingitshane esishushu, ngaphambi kokufika kumda waseArizona ngentsasa yokuqala ngoLwesibini ngamandla eentshingitshane ezitshisayo, ukuze ekugqibeleni inqumle ilizwe laseArizona ize ifike emazantsi eUtah kwangethuba ngoLwesibini ebusuku.
Umngcipheko oyintloko esiwulindeleyo kuRosa okanye kwinto eseleyo kuwo yimvula eninzi kakhulu eBaja California, kumntla-ntshona weSonora nasentlango ekumzantsi-ntshona we-USA, ngokweziko lezikhukula lelizwe.
Kuqikelelwa ukuba imvula iza kubangela imilambo eyingozi nemisinga yenkunkuma kumagqagalana, kuquka ukuchitheka komhlaba kwiindawo ezisezintabeni.
Ukuhlaselwa kweMidsomer Norton: Abane babanjwe ngenxa yokuzama ukubulala
