Amakhulu abantu ababulewe yinyikima netsunami eIndonesia, apho inani labantu abaswelekileyo lisaqhubeka lisanda
Ubuncinane abantu abangama-384 baye bafa, abaninzi babo behluthwe ngamaza amakhulu abetha unxweme, ngenxa yenyikima enkulu kunye netsunami eye yahlasela isiqithi saseIndonesia iSulawesi, urhulumente wathi ngoMgqibelo.
Amakhulu abantu ayehlanganisene ngoLwesihlanu kumnyhadala owawuselunxwemeni kwisixeko sasePalu xa amaza afikelela kwiimitha ezintandathu abetha unxweme ngasekupheleni kosuku, ebhabha abantu abaninzi de bafa yaye esonakalisa yonke into abakuyo.
Le tsunami yalandelwa yinyikima enkulu enobungakanani be-7.5.
Xa isoyikiso se-tsunami safika izolo, abantu babesenza imisebenzi yabo elunxwemeni kwaye abazange babaleke ngoko nangoko.
Utsunami akazange eze yedwa, wahamba neemoto, imithi, izindlu, watshabalalisa yonke into eyayisemhlabeni, watsho uNugroho, esithi utsunami yayihamba ngolwandle oluvulekileyo ngesantya se-800 km/h ngaphambi kokuba ibethe elunxwemeni.
Uthi abanye abantu baye banyuka emthini ukuze baphephe itsunami baza basinda.
Abantu abamalunga ne-16 700 kwafuneka basuswe kwiindawo ezingama-24 ezahlukahlukeneyo ePalu.
Iifoto ezikhutshwe yinqwelo-moya ze-ofisi yokunciphisa iintlekele zibonisa iivenkile ezininzi nezakhiwo ezibhodloziweyo, iibhulorho eziwileyo nezidilikileyo kunye nomzi-mkhosi ojikelezwe ngamanzi.
Isiphango saqhubeka sothusa esi sixeko sinxweme ngoMgqibelo.
Le nyikima yaziva abantu abazizigidi eziyi-2,4 kwelo lizwe.
I-Arhente Yokuvavanya Nokusebenzisa Iteknoloji yaseIndonesia (i-BPPT) yathi kwingxelo yayo, amandla akhululwe yinyikima enkulu yangoLwesihlanu ayephantse aphindwe ka-200 kunamandla ebhombu yeathom eyaphoswa eHiroshima kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Ngokutsho kwe-arhente, iimpawu zendawo yesi sixeko, esisekupheleni kwegxobhozo elide nelisondele, zisenokuba zandisa kakhulu ubungakanani boMtsunami.
UNugroho uchaze umonakalo ngokuthi "ubukhulu" waza wathi amawaka ezindlu, izibhedlele, iivenkile ezinkulu neehotele zidilikile.
Uthi imizimba yamaxhoba yafunyanwa phakathi kwamanxuwa ezakhiwo ezidilikileyo, esithi abantu abangama-540 bonzakele yaye abangama-29 balahlekile.
Ngokutsho kukaNugroho, ukufa nomonakalo kunokuya kwanda kunxweme olungaphaya kweekhilomitha ezingama-300 kumntla wePalu, indawo ebizwa ngokuba yiDonggala, ekufutshane nendawo eyayinenyikima.
Unxibelelwano  lwaphelelwa ngokupheleleyo kwaye ngoko ke akukho naluphi na ulwazi  oluvela eDonggala, utsho uNugroho.
Kukho abantu abangaphezu kwama-300 000 abahlala apho, utshilo uMnqamlezo Olubomvu kwingxelo, esithi abasebenzi bawo namavolontiya ayebhekisa kwiindawo ezichaphazelekayo.
Kwangoku le yintlekele, ngelishwa inokuphela imbi kakhulu, ucinga njalo.
I-arhente yagxekwa kakhulu ngoMgqibelo ngenxa yokungaxeleli nge-tsunami eza ePalu, nangona amagosa athi amaza afika ngexesha ekwakukhutshwa ngalo isilumkiso.
Kwingxelo yomntu othanda ukudlala imidlalo ekwabelwana ngayo kumajelo asekuhlaleni, umntu okwisitezi esiphezulu sesakhiwo unokuviwa ekhwaza ngokungxama elumkisa abantu basesitratweni ngetsunami ezayo.
Kwimizuzu nje embalwa, udonga lwamanzi luqhuma elunxwemeni, lutshabalalisa izakhiwo neenqwelo-mafutha.
I-Reuters ayikwazanga ukuqinisekisa ukuba ngaba le vidiyo yenzekile.
Inyikima kunye netsunami ziye zabangela ukucinywa kombane okuye kwaphazamisa unxibelelwano olujikeleze iPalu, nto leyo ebangela ukuba kube nzima ngamagosa ukuba alungelelanise imisebenzi yohlangulo.
Nangona umkhosi uqalise ukuthumela uncedo lwezezimali ngeenqwelo-moya ezithutha izinto ezisuka eJakarta nakwezinye izixeko, abasemagunyeni bathi abantu abafuduswayo basadinga ukutya, nezinye izinto ezisisiseko.
Isibuko seenqwelo-moya esi sixeko sivulelwe imisebenzi yokunceda kuphela yaye siza kuvalwa kude kube nguOktobha.
UMongameli Joko Widodo wayecwangcisele ukutyelela amaziko abantu abafuduselweyo ePalu ngeCawa.
Inani labantu ababulewe yitsunami yaseIndonesia lingaphezu kwama-800.
Le meko imbi kakhulu.
Nangona abasebenzi beWorld Vision eDonggala bakwazi ukufika bekhuselekile kwisixeko sasePalu, apho abasebenzi bazimela kwiindawo zokukhusela ezenziwe ngelaphu kwiyadi yeofisi yabo, endleleni bafumana imbonakalo yentshabalalo epheleleyo, utsho uDoseba.
"Bandixelele ukuba babone izindlu ezininzi zidiliziwe", watsho.
Le nto iyintlekele.
Nangona amaqela anceda abantu enza isenzo esibuhlungu sokuqalisa umsebenzi wokunceda, abanye abantu bakhalazela ukuba abasebenzi abanceda abantu abahluphekayo abavunyelwa ukuba baye ePalu.
Ngokutsho kwemithetho yaseIndonesia, imali, izinto zokunceda, kunye nabasebenzi abasuka kwamanye amazwe banokuqalisa ukuhla kuphela ukuba indawo yentlekele ibhengezwe njengendawo yentlekele.
Oko akukenzeki.
Kuseyintlekele kwinqanaba lephondo, utshilo uAuliya Arriani, isithethi seRed Cross yaseIndonesia.
Xa urhulumente esithi "kulungile, yintlekele yesizwe", sinokuqalisa ukucela uncedo lwamazwe ngamazwe, kodwa asikabikelwa nqanaba.
Njengoko kwakutshona ubusuku besibini ePalu emva kwenyikima kunye netsunami ngoLwesihlanu, abahlobo nezalamane zabo babengenamntu babeneli themba lokuba ummangaliso uza kwenzeka yaye izalamane zabo ziya kuyiphepha ingxelo ebuhlungu yezi ntlekele.
NgoMgqibelo, kwahlangulwa inkwenkwe eyayibambeke kumjelo wamanzi.
NgeCawa, amaqela okunceda akhulula ibhinqa elaligqunywe phantsi kwamanzi kangangeentsuku ezimbini, lisenegazi likanina.
UGendon Subandono, umqeqeshi weqela lesizwe laseIndonesia lokukhwela ngesikhephe, wayeqeqeshe ababini kwaba bakhweli beenyawo abalahlekileyo kwimidlalo yeAsia, eyaqukunjelwa ekuqaleni kwale nyanga eIndonesia.
Ukongezelela kuMnu. Mandagi, phakathi kwabantu abavalelwe kwihotele iRoa Roa kwakukho nabafundi bakhe.
Njengomntu ophakamileyo kwicandelo leparapente, ndinomthwalo wam wengqondo, walatha.
UMnu. Gendon wachaza ukuba kwiiyure emva kokuba iindaba zokuwa kwehotele iRoa Roa zijikeleze phakathi koluntu lweparapentists, wathumela imiyalezo ngeWhatsApp kwiimvumi zasePalu ezazisemnyhadala waselwandle.
Noko ke, imiyalezo yayibonakala inophawu olungwevu endaweni yophawu oluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka.
Ndicinga ukuba oku kuthetha ukuba imiyalezo ayizange ifike, wongeze watsho.
