UMongameli waseMexico, uAMLO uthembisa ukuba akasayi kusebenzisa amandla omkhosi nxamnye nabemi
UMongameli owanyulweyo waseMexico uAndrés Manuel López Obrador uthembise ukuba akasayi kuze asebenzise umkhosi wokulwa nabantu abaqhelekileyo, njengoko eli lizwe lisondela kumhla wama-50 wokubulawa kwabafundi.
ULopez Obrador wathembisa ngoMgqibelo kwindawo yaseTlatelolco ukuba awusoze uphinde usebenzise amandla omkhosi ukuze ucinezele abantu baseMexico.
Ngo-Oktobha 2, 1968, umkhosi wavusa umlilo ngexesha lomboniso onoxolo kwaye wabulala abantu abangama-300 ngexesha apho iintshukumo zabafundi ezisekhohlo zaziseka iingcambu kulo lonke elaseLatin America.
ULópez Obrador, owatyhola ngokuxhasa ulutsha lwaseMexico ngokunika abafundi imali yokufunda yenyanga nganye nokuvula iiyunivesithi zikarhulumente ezingezizo ezesimahla,
uthi ukungaqeshwa nokungafumani amathuba emfundo kwenza ulutsha lutsaleleke kwiqela elenza ulwaphulo-mthetho.
Ilizwe kufuneka liphinde kabini imali yalo kwi-AI
Njengoko iChina isiya isebenza ngakumbi kwicandelo lobukrelekrele bokuzenzela, iUnited States kufuneka iphinde kabini imali yayo kwicandelo lobukrelekrele bokuzenzela, utshilo uKai-Fu Lee, umtyalomali kunye nengcali yobuchule bokuzenzela osebenzele uGoogle, iMicrosoft neApple.
Ezi ngxelo zivela emva kokuba amalungu aliqela ase-US aqale ukubhengeza amanyathelo malunga ne-AI, nangona ilizwe liswele isicwangciso-qhinga esisemthethweni kwi-AI.
Ngelo xesha, iChina yazisa isicwangciso sayo kunyaka ophelileyo: Injongo yayo kukuba ibe yeyona ndawo iphambili ehlabathini ekuphuhliseni ubuchule bokuzenzela ngowama-2030.
Ukutshintsha imali efunyanwa yiphondo kwi-AI kungasisiqalo esihle, kuba amanye amazwe ashiywe lixesha lilikhulu yi-US kwaye sifuna ukuba ngabokuqala ekuphuhliseni i-AI, utshilo uLee.
Ukuphinda kabini imali kunokuphinda kabini amathuba okuba i-US ifumane into enkulu elandelayo kwi-AI, utshilo uLee kwi-CNBC kudliwano-ndlebe kule veki.
U-Lee, umbhali wencwadi ethi AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order, epapashwe kule nyanga nguHoughton Mifflin Harcourt, uyintloko ye-Sinovation Ventures, eye yatyala imali kwi-Face++, enye yeenkampani eziphambili ze-AI e-China.
Ngonyaka we-1980 wasebenza kwiYunivesithi yaseCarnegie Mellon kwinkqubo ye-AI eyagqitha umdlali waseMelika we-Othello ngeyona nto ibalulekileyo kwaye, kamva, wasebenza njengomphathi kwiMicrosoft Research kunye nomongameli wesebe laseTshayina likaGoogle.
U-Lee wayezixabise kakuhle iimvavanyo zobugcisa zangaphambili zikaRhulumente wase-US, ezinje nge-Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency (DARPA) Robotics Challenge, kwaye wazibuza ukuba uza kwenzeka nini olandelayo ukuze achonge ababoni abalandelayo.
Kukaninzi, abaphandi baseMerika kufuneka basebenze nzima ukuze bafumane imali karhulumente, utshilo uLee.
NgokukaLee, akusiyo iChina ethatha iinkokheli zezemfundo; ziinkampani.
Kwiminyaka yakutshanje, iFacebook, uGoogle nezinye iinkampani zeteknoloji ziye zaqesha abantu ababalaseleyo kwiiyunivesithi ukuba basebenze kwicandelo leAI.
U-Lee wathi umsebenzi wase-US kwi-AI unokuboniswa ukwanda ngokutshintsha komgaqo-nkqubo wokufudukela kwelinye ilizwe.
Ndicinga ukuba amakhadi okuhlala ngokusisigxina kufuneka anikwe abafundi be-PhD kwi-IA, wongeze watsho.
NgoJulayi 2017, iBhunga likaRhulumente laseTshayina lazisa isicwangciso salo sokuphuhlisa ubuchule bokuzenzela.
I-National Natural Science Foundation yase-China inika imali kubantu bamaziko emfundo ngendlela efanayo ne-Natural Science Foundation kunye neminye imibutho karhulumente yase-US inika imali kubaphandi base-US, kodwa umgangatho womsebenzi wezemfundo uphantsi kune-China, utshilo uLee.
Ekuqaleni konyaka, iSebe lezoKhuselo laseUnited States laseka iZiko eliDibeneyo le-Artificial Intelligence, elenzelwe ukuba kubandakanywe abasebenzi abavela kwicandelo loshishino nakumaziko ezifundo, kwaye iNdlu ye-White yamemezela ukusekwa kweKomiti ekhethiweyo ye-Artificial Intelligence.
Kwakhona, kule nyanga i-DARPA ibhengeze utyalomali lwe-$2 billion kwiphulo elibizwa ngokuba yi-AI Next.
Ngokuphathelele iNatural Science Foundation, ngoku ibeka ngaphezu kwe-100 yezigidi zeedola ngonyaka kuphando lwe-AI.
Okwangoku, sekudlule iinyanga kungekho nto yenziwayo ngokuphathelele umthetho waseMerika owawufuna ukuseka iKomishoni Yokhuseleko Lwelizwe Kwi-Artificial Intelligence.
Abantu baseMacedonia benza intetho yesigqibo malunga nokutshintsha igama lelizwe
NgeCawa abantu baseMakedoni baqhuba irhafu yokhetho ngokutshintsha igama labo libe yi "Republic of North Macedonia", isenzo esiza kusombulula imbambano esele ikho kangangamashumi eminyaka neGrisi, ebikade ibhloka izicelo zeMakedoni zokungena kwi-EU nakwi-NATO.
IGrisi, enesithili esibizwa ngokuba yiMakedoni, ithi igama lommelwane wayo osemantla libonisa ukuba iyakufuna ukuba lilungu leNATO ne-EU.
NgoJuni, oorhulumente bobabini bafikelela kwisivumelwano ngegama elitsha, kodwa abachasi besizwe bathi utshintsho luya kutshabalalisa ubuhlanga babantu baseMakedoni.
UMongameli uGeorge Ivanov uthe akazukuthatha inxaxheba kule referendum, kwaye iphulo lokuyichasa libonisa ukuba akunakwenzeka ukuba afikelele kwinani elincinane lama-50% ukuze le referendum isebenze.
Umbuzo okwiphepha lendibano uthi: Uyayixhasa into yokuba lilungu leNATO ne-EU, xa wamkela isivumelwano neGrisi?
Abaxhasi beli gama, kuquka iNkulumbuso uZoran Zaev, bathi lixabiso elifanelekileyo lokufikelela ekujoyini iMakedoni, elinye lamazwe awabakho emva kokwahlukana kweYugoslavia, kwimibutho efana ne-EU ne-NATO.
Namhlanje ndize kuvota ngekamva lelizwe, ukuze ulutsha lwaseMakedoni luphile ngokukhululekileyo kumzantsi we-EU, kuba oko kuthetha ukuba sonke siza kuba nobomi obukhuselekileyo, utshilo uOlivera Georgijevska, oneminyaka engama-79, eSkopje.
Nangona ingekho mthethweni, inani elaneleyo lamalungu ePalamente libonise ukuba liza kuyamkela imiphumo yokuvota ukuze ibe yinto ebalulekileyo.
Ukutshintsha igama, kufuneka isibini esithathwini senani lePalamente.
IKomishoni yoNyulo yeLizwe inike ingxelo yokuba akukho nto iphosakeleyo yenzekileyo ngentsimbi yeshumi elinanye.
Nangona kunjalo, inxaxheba yayingu-16%, xa kuthelekiswa nama-34% abhaliswe kunyulo lwaseburhulumenteni oludlulileyo, olwalubanjwa ngo-2016, apho abantu abangama-66% ababhalisiweyo bavota.
Ndize kuvota ngabantwana bam, indawo yethu iseYurophu, watsho uGjose Tanevski, oneminyaka engama-62 ubudala, kwikomkhulu, eSkopje.
Inkulumbuso yaseMakedoni, uZoran Zaev, umfazi wakhe uZorica nonyana wakhe uDushko bavotele irekhodi lokuvota kwilizwe laseMakedoni malunga nokutshintsha igama lelizwe, eliza kuvula indlela yokuba lilungu le-European Union kunye ne-NATO eStrumica, eMakedoni, nge-30 kaSeptemba 2018.
Phambi kwePalamente yaseSkopje, uVladimir Kavardarkov, oneminyaka engama-54 ubudala, wayelungisa isiteji esincinane waza wabeka izitulo phambi kweentente ezazimiselwe abantu abaza kuyikhaba le referendum.
Sifuna iNATO ne-EU, kodwa sifuna ukungena ngayo ngentloko ephakamileyo, hayi ngomnyango ongasemva, utshilo uKavadarkov.
Sililizwe elihlwempuzekileyo, kodwa sinesidima.
Ukuba abafuni ukusamkela njengeMakedoni, sinokuya kwamanye amazwe, njenge China ne Russia, size sibe yinxalenye yokudityaniswa kwe-Eurasian.
Inkulumbuso uZaev ithi ukujoyina iNATO kuza kuhamba notyalo-mali olungakumbi eMakedoni, enenani elingaphezulu kwama-20 ekhulwini labantu abangasebenziyo.
Ndicinga ukuba uninzi lwabantu luza kuvota ngenxa yokuba bangaphezu kwama-80% abemi abaxhasa i-EU ne-NATO, watsho uZaev ngaphambi kokuba abeke phantsi iphepha lakhe.
UZaev wathi Ewe wayeza kuba ukuqinisekiswa kwekamva lethu.
Uphando olwenziwe ngoMvulo liZiko Lophando Ngezopolitiko laseMakedoni lubonisa ukuba phakathi kwe-30% ne-43% yabavoti baza kuthatha inxaxheba kule referendum, eli nani lingaphantsi kwenani elifunekayo.
Ngokutsho kolunye uhlolisiso olwenziwa yiTelma TV yaseMakedoni, ama-57% abo baphendulileyo bacinga ukuba baza kuvota ngeCawa.
Kulawo, ama-70% athi aya kuvota Ewe.
Ukuze intetho yesigqibo isebenze, kufuneka kubekho abantu abangama-50% kunye nevoto enye.
Ukuphulukana nenkundla yesigqibo kuya kuba ngumqobo wokuqala kumgaqo-nkqubo kaRhulumente othanda iNtshona ukususela oko wathatha isikhundla ngoMeyi wonyaka ophelileyo.
