John Edward: Izakhono zolwimi zibalulekile kubemi behlabathi
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland zigcina umkhondo wokugqwesa kwizifundo eziye zaqhubeka ngo-2018 ngolunye uthotho lweziphumo zeemviwo ezigqwesileyo, ezomelezwa yimpumelelo yomntu ngamnye neqela kwezemidlalo, ubugcisa, umculo kunye neminye imizamo yoluntu.
Ngaphezulu kwabafundi abangama-30,000 kulo lonke elaseScotland, ezi zikolo, ezimelwe liBhunga laseScotland leZikolo eziZimeleyo (SCIS) zizama ukubonelela ngenkonzo esemgangathweni kubafundi nakubazali.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zenzelwe ukulungiselela abafundi ukuba bafunde eminye imfundo, bafumane umsebenzi abawukhethayo, baze babe ngabemi behlabathi.
Njengommandla wemfundo onokwakha nokuphumeza ikharityhulam yesikolo esenziwe ngokwezifiso, sibona ukuba iilwimi zanamhlanje zisaqhubeka ziyinto ethandwa kakhulu nefunwa kakhulu ezikolweni.
UNelson Mandela wathi, "Ukuba uthetha nomntu ngolwimi aluqondayo, uya kufikelela entlokweni yakhe.
Ukuba uthetha naye ngolwimi lwakhe, uya kufikelela entliziyweni yakhe.
Esi sisikhumbuzo esibalulekileyo sokuba asinakuxhomekeka kwisiNgesi kuphela ukuba sifuna ukwakha ubudlelwane nokwakha intembeko nabantu bamanye amazwe.
Ngokutsho kweziphumo zakutshanje zeemviwo zalo nyaka, siyabona ukuba iilwimi zikhokela kwizibalo zezona zikolo zizimeleyo ziphumelele kakhulu.
Ama-68% abafundi abafunda iilwimi zasemzini bafumana amanqaku aphezulu.
Idatha, eqokelelwe kwizikolo ezingama-74 ezingamalungu e-SCIS yabonisa ukuba ama-72% abafundi bafumana amanqaku aphezulu kwi-Mandarin, ngelixa ama-72% abafundi baseJamani, ama-69% abafundi baseFrentshi kunye nama-63% abafundi baseSpain bafumana amanqaku aphezulu.
Oku kubonisa ukuba izikolo ezizimeleyo eScotland zixhasa iilwimi zangaphandle njengezakhono ezibalulekileyo abantwana nolutsha abaya kuthi ngokuqinisekileyo balufune kwixesha elizayo.
Namhlanje, iilwimi, njengesifundo esikhethiweyo, zigcinwa zikwindawo enye nezifundo ze-STEM (inzululwazi, iteknoloji, ubunjineli nemathematika) kwizicwangciso zezifundo ezikolweni ezizimeleyo nakwezinye iindawo.
Uphando olwenziwe ngo-2014 yiKomishoni yezeMisebenzi kunye neZakhono yase-UK yabonisa ukuba kwizizathu abaqeshi abazinika ukuba kunzima ukuzalisa izithuba, iipesenti ezili-17 zachazwa ngokungabikho kobugcisa bolwimi.
Ngoko ke, izakhono zolwimi ziya zanda ukuze kulungiselelwe ulutsha imisebenzi yalo yexesha elizayo.
Njengoko amathuba emisebenzi efuna iilwimi esanda, ezi zakhono zibalulekile kwihlabathi eliguqukayo.
Kungakhathaliseki ukuba ukhetha wuphi umsebenzi, ukuba ufunde ulwimi lwesibini, uya kuba nempembelelo enkulu kwixesha elizayo xa unolwazi olunjalo.
Ukukwazi ukuthetha nabantu abakwamanye amazwe ngokuzenzekelayo kubeka umntu othetha iilwimi ezininzi phambi kwabanye.
Ngokutsho kophando olwenziwa ngo-2013 nguYouGov kubantu abadala abangaphezu kwama-4,000 e-UK, ama-75 ekhulwini babengakwazi ukuthetha ulwimi lwasemzini kakuhle ngokwaneleyo ukuba banxibelelane, yaye isiFrentshi, esinabantu abali-15% abathetha ulwimi, yayilulwimi kuphela olwalunamanani amanani aphindwe kabini.
Kungenxa yoko le nto ukutyala imali ekufundiseni ulwimi kubalulekile kubantwana namhlanje.
Ukwazi iilwimi ezininzi, ingakumbi ezo zezoqoqosho eziphuhlileyo, kuya kunika abantwana ithuba elingcono lokufumana umsebenzi obalulekileyo.
IScotland inezinto ezahlukeneyo ezenziwa kwizikolo malunga neelwimi ezifundiswayo.
Ezinye izikolo zigxininisa ngakumbi kwiilwimi zanamhlanje nezasendulo, ngelixa ezinye zifundisa iilwimi ezijongwa njengeziya kubaluleka kwi-UK kwixesha elizayo, malunga no-2020, ezinje ngesiMandarin okanye isiJapan.
Enoba yintoni umntwana wakho ayifunayo, unokukhetha phakathi kweelwimi ezikwizikolo ezizimeleyo, ezinabafundisi abaziingcali kulo mba.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland zizimisele ukubonelela ngendawo yokufunda eya kulungiselela abantwana kwaye ibanike izakhono ezifunekayo ukuze baphumelele, nokuba kwenzeka ntoni na kwixesha elizayo.
Kwimeko yorhwebo lwehlabathi namhlanje, akunakuphikwa ukuba iilwimi zisenokubaluleka kakhulu kwikamva lelizwe, kwaye oku kufuneka kubonakaliswe kwimfundo.
Enyanisweni, iilwimi zanamhlanje kufuneka zithathwe njengezakhono zonxibelelwano zamazwe ngamazwe.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo ziya kuqhubeka zinika olu khetho, iyantlukwano kunye nokugqwesa kulutsha lwaseScotland.
Kufuneka yenziwe kakuhle.
