ULeBron uza kudlala iLakers eSan Diego ngeCawa
Ukulinda phantse kuphelile kubalandeli abafuna ukubona uLeBron James edlala umdlalo wakhe wokuqala neLos Angeles Lakers.
Umqeqeshi weLakers, uLuke Walton, ubhengeze ukuba uJames uza kudlala umdlalo wokuqala wexesha lonyaka ngeCawa nxamnye neDenver Nuggets eSan Diego.
Kodwa kusafuneka kugqitywe ukuba uza kudlala imizuzu emingaphi.
"Kuza kuba ngaphezu kweyodwa nangaphantsi kwama-48", watsho uWalton kwiWebhsayithi yaseLakers.
UMike Trudell, intatheli yeLakers, watyhila ukuba mhlawumbi uJames uza kudlala imizuzu embalwa.
Emva koqeqesho ekuqaleni kwale veki, uJames wabuzwa malunga nezicwangciso zakhe zeshedyuli yemidlalo emithandathu yexesha langaphambi kwexesha leLakers.
"Andifuni imidlalo yangaphambi kwexesha kule nqanaba lomsebenzi wam ukuze ndibe ngcono", watsho.
Intlanganiso kaTrump eNtshona Virginia, Ijelo leYouTube
Umongameli uDonald Trump uqalisa umlo weengxoxo ngokuhlwa nje eWheeling, eWest Virginia.
Le yindibano yokuqala kwezintlanu zikaTrump ezicwangciselwe iveki ezayo, eziquka ukutyelela iindawo ezinomdla, njengeTennessee neMississippi.
Ngoxa kuvotelwa ukuba ngubani oza kuvala isithuba kwiNkundla Ephakamileyo, uTrump uzimisele ukufumana inkxaso kunyulo oluzayo lwaphakathi kwethemu, njengoko amaRephabliki esengozini yokulahlekelwa lulawulo lweCongress xa kuvota ngoNovemba.
Lithini ixesha lentlanganiso kaTrump yaseWest Virginia ngokuhlwanje kwaye inokubonwa njani kwi-intanethi?
Intlanganiso kaTrump eWheeling, eWest Virginia, imiselwe iiyure ezisi-7 namhlanje, ngoMgqibelo, nge-29 kaSeptemba 2018.
Intlanganiso kaTrump yaseWest Virginia inokubonwa kwi-intanethi kule khonkco ingezantsi, ngevidiyo esasazwa ngqo kwiYouTube.
Kusenokwenzeka ukuba uTrump uza kuxoxa ityala eliqale kule veki lomntu otyunjwe kwiNkundla Ephakamileyo, uBrett Kavanaugh, obekade exinezelekile ngenxa yezityholo zokuxhatshazwa ngokwesondo ajamelana nazo, ngoxa ukuvotelwa kwakhe yiSenate kusalinde iveki enye yaye iFBI iphando ngale meko.
Kodwa eyona njongo yale ntlanganiso kukunceda amaRephabliki alindele unyulo lukaNovemba.
Ngoko ke, iintlanganiso ezintlanu zephulo likaMongameli Trump ezicwangciselwe iveki ezayo zijolise ekuvuseleleni amavolontiya nabaxhasi, ngoxa amaRephabliki ezama ukukhusela nokwandisa ubukhulu bawo kwiNdlu yeeNgwevu nakwiNdlu yabameli, ngokutsho kweReuters.
"Ukulawula iCongress kubaluleke kakhulu kwi-ajenda yakhe kangangokuba umongameli uza kuhamba kumazwe amaninzi njengoko enako, njengoko sisingise kwixesha elixakekileyo lokuvota", utshilo isithethi sikaTrump esingafuni kuchazwa igama, ngokutsho kweReuters.
Intlanganiso yangokuhlwa, ecwangciselwe iWesbanco Arena, eWheeling, inokuhlanganisa abaxhasi abaseOhio nasePennsylvania, kwaye itsale inkcazelo kumajelo eendaba asePittsburgh, ngokutsho kweWest Virginia Metro News.
NgoMgqibelo iya kuba lixesha lesibini uTump etyelela iWest Virginia, ilizwe awaphumelela kulo ngaphezulu kwama-40 ekhulwini leepesenti ngowama-2016.
UTrump uzama ukunceda uPatrick Morrisey, umgqatswa weRepublican kwiSenate yaseWest Virginia, ophumelela kakubi kwiipoll.
"Asikho isalathiso esihle sokuba uMorissey afune ukuba umongameli amkhuthaze kwiipolls", utshilo uSimon Haeder, isazi sezopolitiko kwiYunivesithi yaseWest Virginia, ngokutsho kweReuters.
I-Ryder Cup 2018: Iqela laseMerika libonisa ukuzimisela ukugcina amathemba ephila xa kujongwa imidlalo yomntu ngamnye ngeCawa
Emva kweeseshoni ezintathu ezingalinganiyo, ii-foursomes zangemva kwemini ngoMgqibelo mhlawumbi yayiyinto eyayifuneka kule Ryder Cup.
I-pendulum ye-dynamics yezemidlalo yinto eyenziwe ngabantu, abadlali bayakholelwa kuyo, ngakumbi kwimidlalo efana nale.
Ngoko ke, liliphi icala elihamba kakuhle ngoku?
Bebenezinto ezintandathu eziphambili kwaye ngoku zine, ngoko ndicinga ukuba sikwicala elihle, watsho uJordan Spieth njengoko wayehamba ekupheleni kosuku.
Ngokucacileyo, iYurophu inenzuzo, inamanqaku amane phambili, inamanqaku ali-12 ngaphezulu.
AmaMerika, njengoko uSpieth esitsho, avakalelwa kukuba umoya uvuthuza kancinci ngakwabo kwaye banezizathu ezininzi zokukhuthazeka, ikakhulu ngenxa yemeko yefom kaSpieth noJustin Thomas, abadlale kunye imini yonke kwaye bobabini banezinto ezintathu ezine.
USpieth uye wabulala ukususela ekuqaleni ukuya kutsho kumhlaba omdaka yaye ubeka umzekelo omhle.
Imikhwazo yokugubha yenyuka ngamandla njengoko wayeqhubeka nomjikelo wakhe waza wafumana iputts ebalulekileyo yokutshatisa umdlalo wesine, xa yena noThomas babephantsi emva kwemingxunya emibini.
Wayibhiyozela iputts eyabenza baphumelela umdlalo kwi-15 hole ngomkhala ofanayo, ngendlela ebonisa ukuba ukholelwa ukuba iqela laseMelika alikaphumi kukhuphiswano.
Umele uzame ngamandla akho onke kwaye ukhathalele iqela lakho, walatha uSpieth.
Yinto yonke abanayo aba badlali ngoku.
Imingxunya eli-18 yokubeka iimpuphu.
Abona badlali banamanqaku amaninzi kunoSpieth noThomas kwiintsuku ezimbini ezidlulileyo nguFrancesco Molinari noTommy Fleetwood, imvakalelo engenakuphikiswa yeRyder Cup.
Esi sibini singaqhelekanga kodwa sithandekayo saseYurophu sinxiba ezine kwezine yaye asizenzi iimpazamo.
Moliwood babe kuphela kwesibini esingazange senze i-bogey ngoMgqibelo emva kwemini, kwaye kwakhona bayiphepha i-bogey ngoMgqibelo ekuseni nangomgqibelo emva kwemini, kunye ne-last nine holes ngoLwesihlanu ekuseni.
Ngenxa yesi siphumo nendlela amandla akhe abonakala ngathi ayahamba ngayo ukuya nokubuya kwesihlwele esiphithizelayo, uyaqinisekisa ukuba ngabadlali ababetha ngeCawa, kwaye akukho mdlali uthandwayo njengoFleetwood okanye uMolinari ukuvala uloyiso olunokwenzeka lwaseYurophu njengoko ilanga litshona kwiLe Golf National.
Kungcono zombini ngaxeshanye kumagumbi ahlukeneyo.
Noko ke, ukuthetha ngozuko lwaseYurophu kwakubonakala kungekudala.
UBubba Watson noWebb Simpson bagqiba ngokukhawuleza uSergio Garcia, iqhawe le-fourballs yasekuseni, owatshata noAlex Noren.
I-bogey kunye namabini aphindwe kabini kumngxuma wokuqala omathandathu, yafaka iSpanish neSweden kumngxuma abangenakho ukuphuma kuwo.
Kodwa ngeCawa, akukho mntu unokukunceda uphume emhadini.
Iifurballs ne-foursomes zinomdla kakhulu ukubukela indlela izixhobo ezisebenza ngayo, iingcebiso ezinikayo nezingakunikiyo, nendlela isicwangciso esingatshintsha ngayo ngesiquphe.
Ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, iYurophu idlale kakuhle njengeqela kwaye iza kudlala usuku lokugqibela inenzuzo enkulu, kodwa esi siganeko sokudlala sibonisa ukuba iqela laseMelika linomdla wokulwa abanye, ngakumbi eMelika, ababekhe babuza.
IYurophu ifikelela kumdlalo wokugqibela weRyder Cup ngamanqaku alungileyo ayi-10-6
IYurophu iza kujongana nosuku lokugqibela lweRyder Cup inethuba elifanelekileyo emva kokugqiba imidlalo ye-fourballs ne-foursomes ngoMgqibelo ngempumelelo eyi-10-6 phezu kwe-United States.
I-duo ephefumlelweyo eyenziwe nguTommy Fleetwood noFrancesco Molinari benza umzamo omkhulu wokufumana uloyiso ezimbini ngokuchasene noTiger Woods onzima kwaye ushiye irekhodi lakhe, ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, kumanqaku amane eLe Golf National.
Iqela laseYurophu, elalikhokelwa nguThomas Bjorn, elalifuna ukugcina indebe elaliyibethe kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo eHazeltine, lalawula iqela laseMerika elalingakhange lichaneke kakuhle kwii-fourballs zasekuseni laza labeka uthotho ngo-3-1.
I-USA yabonisa umlo omkhulu kwii-foursomes kwaye yaphumelela imidlalo emibini, kodwa ayikwazanga ukunciphisa umahluko.
Iqela likaJim Furyk lalidinga ukufumana amanqaku asibhozo kwimidlalo eli-12 yomntu ngamnye ngeCawa ukuze ligcine indebe.
UFleetwood ngowokuqala umqalayo waseYurophu ukufumana amanqaku amane ngokulandelelana, ngelixa yena noMolinari, ababizwa ngegama elithi Molliwood emva kwempelaveki entle, bangesibini nje isibini esifumana amanqaku amane kwimidlalo yaso yokuqala emine kwimbali yeRyder Cup.
Emva kokubetha uWoods noPatrick Reed kwii-fourballs, benza umboniso oqaqambileyo wokubetha uWoods ongenampilo kunye nomqali wokuqala waseMelika uBryson Dechambeau ngo-5&4 obaluleke ngakumbi.
UWoods, owayekrwitsha kwimidlalo emibini ngoMgqibelo, wabonisa izibane zobugcisa, kodwa waphulukana nemidlalo eli-19 kwimi-29 kwii-fourballs nakwi-foursomes, nemidlalo esixhenxe elandelelanayo.
UJustin Rose, owayengekho kwii-fourballs zasekuseni, waphinda wadibana noHenrik Stenson kwii-foursomes waza wawa ngo-2-1 kuDustin Johnson noBrooks Koepka, ababekwindawo yokuqala neyesithathu kwihlabathi, ngokwahlukeneyo.
Noko ke, iYurophu yayingenayo yonke into eyayibekwe phambi kwayo ngomhla omnandi nofudumeleyo kumzantsi-ntshona weParis.
UJordan Spieth, ophumelele kathathu kolu khuphiswano, noJustin Thomas ngoMgqibelo babeka umda kumaMerika ngokufumana amanqaku amabini.
Bafumana uloyiso olunzima ngo-2-1 nxamnye neSpanish Jon Rahm noIan Poulter kwii-fourballs kwaye kamva baphinda baphumelela uPoulter noRory McIlroy ngo-4-3 kwii-foursomes, emva kokuphulukana nemingxunya yokuqala emibini.
Kuphela kabini kwimbali yeRyder Cup iqela lalisele libuyele umva umahluko wamanqaku amane kwimidlalo yabantu, nangona iqela likaFuryk, umkhuseli wetayitile, lifuna kuphela ukudibanisa ukuze liyigcine.
Nangona kunjalo, emva kokuba ngowesibini obalaseleyo kwiintsuku ezimbini, kubonakala ngathi ukuhlasela kwakhona ngeCawa ezayo kuphandle kwendlela yakhe.
UMntla Korea uthi awuyi kulahla izixhobo zawo ngokungenakuze  ukuba awunakufumana imiqondiso yokuthembela
UMphathiswa Wezangaphandle waseMntla Korea uxelele iZizwe Ezimanyeneyo ngoMgqibelo ukuba izohlwayo eziqhubekayo zenza ukuba abantu bangathembi iUnited States yaye phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo, ilizwe aliyi kuziphelisa ngaxeshanye izixhobo zalo zenyukliya.
URi Yong Ho waxelela i-World Health Organization Annual General Assembly ukuba i-North Korea ithathe "amanyathelo abalulekileyo entando entle" kunyaka ophelileyo, njengokuyeka uvavanyo lwentolo yenyukliya neyenkanyamba, ukuvala indawo yovavanyo lwentolo yenyukliya nokuzibophelela ekungasasazeni izixhobo zenyukliya nobuchwepheshe.
Nangona kunjalo, asiboni mpendulo ivumelana ne-US, utshilo.
Ngaphandle kokuthembela eMelika, akusayi kubakho ntembelo kukhuseleko lwethu lwesizwe kwaye, phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo, asiyi kuqalisa ukulwa ngokwasemthethweni nangayiphi na indlela.
Nangona uRi wazikhalimela izikhalazo ezaziwayo zaseMntla Korea malunga nokuxhathisa kweWashington kwindlela yokucwangcisa ngamanqanaba apho iNorth Korea yayiya kuvuzwa njengoko yayithatha amanyathelo ngokuthe ngcembe, iingxelo zakhe zabonakala zibalulekile kuba akazange ayilahle ngokupheleleyo into yokucwangcisa ngokuthe ngqo, njengoko kwakwenziwe yiPyongyang ngaphambili.
URi wabhekisela kwingxelo edibeneyo eyenziwa nguKim Jong Un noDonald Trump kwintlanganiso yokuqala phakathi komongameli wase-US nolawulo lwaseMntla Korea eSingapore ngoJuni 12, apho uKim wazinikela ekusebenzeni kwenza iNduli yaseKorea , ngelixa uTrump wathembisa iziqinisekiso zokhuseleko lwaseMntla Korea.
UMntla Korea uzame ukuwuphelisa ngokusemthethweni iMfazwe yaseKorea yowe-1950-53, kodwa iUnited States ithe kuqala iPyongyang kufuneka isuse izixhobo zayo zenyukliya.
IWashington nayo iye yamelana nemfuno yokunciphisa izigwebo ezinzima zamazwe ngamazwe ezibekwe kwiNyakatho Korea.
I-US igxininisa ukuba kufuneka kuqala kwenziwe ukulwa ne-nuclear kwaye inyusa inqanaba loxinzelelo ngezohlwayo ukufezekisa injongo yayo ngendlela enyanzelisayo, ukongeza ekumelaneni nokuvakaliswa kokuphela kwemfazwe, utshilo uRi.
Ingcamango yokuba izigwebo ziya kusenza siguqe ngamadolo yinto nje abantu abangayaziyo ngathi.
Kodwa ingxaki kukuba izigwebo eziqhubekayo zenza singathembi mntu.
URi akazange athethe ngecebo lokubamba intlanganiso yesibini kaKim noTrump eyathethwa yinkokeli yaseMelika kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo ekuqaleni kwale veki.
Endaweni yoko, umphathiswa wakhankanya iintlanganiso ezintathu phakathi kukaKim kunye nenkokeli yaseMzantsi Korea uMun Jae-in kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo waza wongeza: Ukuba iqela elibandakanyekayo kumcimbi wokupheliswa kwenyukliya yayinguMzantsi Korea endaweni ye-US, ukupheliswa kwenyukliya kwinxweme laseKorea bekungayi kufika kule meko yokuma.
Nangona kunjalo, ithoni yentetho kaRi yayahluke kakhulu kunyaka ophelileyo, xa wathi kwiNdibano Jikelele yeZizwe eziManyeneyo ukuba ukujolisa kumhlaba waseMelika ngeentolo zaseMntla Korea kwakungenakuphepheka emva kokuba uMongameli Mr. Evil Trump ebize uKim Rocket Man kumsebenzi wokuzibulala.
Kulo nyaka kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo, uTrump, owathi kunyaka ophelileyo wasongela ukutshabalalisa ngokupheleleyo iNyakatho Korea, wancoma uKim ngesibindi sakhe sokuthatha amanyathelo okulahla izixhobo kodwa wathi kusekuninzi ekusafuneka kwenziwe kwaye izohlwayo kufuneka zisekwe de iNyakatho Korea isuse izixhobo zenyukliya.
NgoLwesithathu odlulileyo, uTrump wathi akukho xesha limisiweyo loku, kwaye "akukho ngxaki ukuba kuthatha iminyaka emibini, emithathu okanye iinyanga ezintlanu".
I-China neRashiya zithi iBhunga loKhuseleko le-UN lifanele livuze iPyongyang ngamanyathelo ethathiweyo.
Nangona kunjalo, uNobhala welizwe wase-US, uMike Pompeo, uthe ngoLwesine kwiBhunga loKhuseleko le-UN: Ukunyanzeliswa kwezohlwayo zeBhunga loKhuseleko kufuneka kuqhubeke ngamandla kwaye ngaphandle kokukhetha de siqinisekise ukuphelelwa kwenyukliya ngokupheleleyo nangokugqibeleleyo.
INgqungquthela yoKhuseleko iye yavumelana ngokuwisa izigwebo kuMntla Korea ukususela ngo-2006 ukuze inqande inkxaso-mali yeenkqubo zeentolo zenyukliya nezentakumba zasePyongyang.
UPompeo wadibana noRi ngaphandle kweNdibano Jikelele yeZizwe Ezimanyeneyo waza emva koko wachazela ukuba uza kuphinda atyelele iPyongyang kwinyanga ezayo ukulungiselela intlanganiso yesibini.
UPompeo sele etyelele eMntla Korea kathathu kulo nyaka, kodwa uhambo lwakhe lokugqibela aluhambanga kakuhle.
Washiya iPyongyang ngoJulayi esithi kubekho inkqubela eyenziweyo, kodwa emva kweeyure ezimbalwa iNorth Korea yamtyhola ngokwenza "iimfuno ezinje ngezigebenga".
Kwintlanganiso eyayibanjwe noMoon kule nyanga, uMntla Korea wathembisa ukuchitha indawo yayo yokulwa neentsholongwane zenyukliya ukuba iUnited States ithatha "amanyathelo afanelekileyo".
Wathi uKim wayemxelele ukuba Izinyathelo ezihambelanayo azifunayo zizinyathelo zokhuseleko uTrump azithembise eSingapore, ukongeza kwimisebenzi yokubuyisela ubudlelwane bube busemgangathweni neWashington.
Abafundi baseHarvard benza ikhosi yokufunda indlela yokuphumla
Kulo nyaka uphelileyo, iHarvard University iye yavula ikhosi entsha yokufundisa abafundi bayo ukuba balale ixesha elide, ukuze ilwe nenkcubeko eyonakeleyo yokufunda ubusuku bonke, ekhuthazwa yikhefi.
Omnye umphengululi waphawula ukuba abafundi abakwiyunivesithi ekumgangatho ophezulu ehlabathini badla ngokungazazi izinto ezisisiseko ngendlela yokuzinyamekela.
UCharles Czeisler, unjingalwazi wezoNyango lweSleep kwiSikolo sezoNyango saseHarvard kunye nengcali kwiSibhedlele saseBrigham and Women, wayila ikhosi, ekholelwa ukuba yeyokuqala yohlobo lwayo eUnited States.
Wafumana inkuthazo yokwenza le khosi emva kokunikela intetho malunga nefuthe lokungalali kakuhle ekufundeni.
Emva kokuba ndigqibile ukuthetha, kweza intombazana yathi, "Kutheni undixelela le nto nje, kunyaka wam wokugqibela?"
Wathi akukho mntu wakha wathetha naye ngokubaluleka kokulala, nto leyo eyandothusayo, watsho kwiThe Telegraph.
Le khosi, eyaqala ukusetyenziswa kulo nyaka, ifundisa abafundi izinto ezisisiseko ngendlela indlela yokulala elungileyo enokuphucula ngayo impumelelo yabo kwizifundo nakwizemidlalo, kuquka nokuba sempilweni.
UPaul Barreira, ongunjingalwazi wezifo zengqondo kwiHarvard Medical School nomlawuli olawulayo weenkonzo zempilo kwiyunivesithi, wathi le yunivesithi yagqiba kwelokuba izise le khosi emva kokufumanisa ukuba abanye abafundi bafumana ubunzima bokungalali ngexesha leveki.
Ikhosi, yeyure enye, ibandakanya uthotho lwemisebenzi yokunxibelelana.
Kwelinye icandelo kukho umfanekiso wegumbi lokulala, apho abafundi kufuneka bacofe iikomityi zekofu, amakhethini, iibhedi, neencwadi ukuze bafumane inkcazelo ngemiphumo yecaffeine nokukhanya, indlela ukulala ngokwaneleyo okuchaphazela ngayo ukusebenza kwezemidlalo, nokubaluleka kokugcina ixesha lokulala.
Kwelinye icandelo, abaphulaphuli bayafundiswa ngendlela ukulala ixesha elide okunokubenza babe sengozini yokuhlaselwa yintliziyo, ukuphazamiseka, ukudandatheka nomhlaza.
Emva koko, imephu yekhampasi enezithonjana ezinomdla ikhuthaza abathathi-nxaxheba ukuba bacinge ngendlela yabo yemihla ngemihla.
Siyazi ukuba indlela abaziphatha ngayo abafundi ayizukutshintsha ngoko nangoko.
Kodwa sikholelwa ukuba banelungelo lokwazi, kanye njengokuba umntu enelungelo lokwazi ngemiphumo yokutshaya icuba emzimbeni wakhe, utshilo uProfesa Czeisler.
Wathi, "Ibango lokuhlala uphaphile ubusuku bonke lisekho", yaye wathi iteknoloji yanamhlanje nengcinezelo ekhulayo kubafundi yenza ukuba ukulala kungabi yingxaki.
Ukuqinisekisa ukuba ulala ngokwaneleyo ngexesha elide kufanele kube sisisombululo esifihlakeleyo kubafundi sokulwa noxinzelelo, ukudinwa noxinzelelo, wongezelela, kwanokukhusela ukwanda kwesisindo, kuba ukulala ngokwaneleyo kubeka ingqondo kwimodi yokulala kwaye kwenza abafundi bahlale belambile.
URaymond So, umfana waseCalifornia oneminyaka eli-19 ubudala ofunda iChemistry neBiology Physical, wanceda uProfesa Czeisler ukuyila ikhosi, emva kokuya kwelinye leeklasi zakhe kunyaka wakhe wokugqibela kunyaka wakhe wokuqala eHarvard.
URaymond wathi le khosi yamvula amehlo waza waphefumlelwa ukuba ayikhuthaze yonke ikhampasi.
Uthe inyathelo elilandelayo kukucela abafundi abaphumelele kwizikolo eziphakamileyo ukuba benze inkqubo efanayo ngaphambi kokuba bajoyine iziko elikhuphisanayo.
UNjingalwazi Czeisler wacebisa abafundi ukuba bakhumbule ukubeka isilumkiso xa belala naxa bevuka, nokuba bazi ngemiphumo emibi yokukhanya okuluhlaza okukhutshwa ziikrini ze-elektroniki nezibane ze-LED, ezinokuphazamisa ukuvisisana kwemijikelo yemini yaye zibangele iingxaki zokulala.
