Isitofu esitsha sokuthintela umhlaza sinokufundisa amajoni omzimba ukubona iiseli ezinobungozi
Isitofu esitsha sokuthintela umhlaza sinokufundisa amajoni omzimba ukuba abone aze atshabalalise iiseli ezinobungozi
I-vaccine ifundisa amajoni omzimba ukuba azi iiseli ezinobungozi njengenxalenye yonyango
Le ndlela iquka ukuthatha iiseli zomzimba kumguli uze uzitshintshe kwilebhu
Unokujonga iprotheyini eqhelekileyo kumhlaza uze uyifake kwakhona
Isitofu sokugonya esivavanywayo sibonisa iziphumo ezithembisayo kwizigulana ezinomhlaza ohlukeneyo.
Elinye ibhinqa elalinikwe eli yeza, elifundisa amajoni omzimba ukuba azi iiseli ezinobungozi, lafumana isifo somhlaza wesibeleko sapheliswa kwiinyanga ezili-18.
Le ndlela iquka ukuthatha iiseli zomzimba kumguli, uzitshintshe kwilebhu ukuze "ubone" iprotheni ekhoyo kwiintlobo ezininzi zomhlaza (HER2) uze emva koko uzifake kwakhona.
Ngokutsho kukaNjingalwazi Jay Berzofsky weNational Cancer Institute eBethesda, eMaryland, eUnited States, "Iziphumo esizifumeneyo zibonisa ukuba sinegciwane elithembisayo".
Uprofesa Berzofsky uthi, iprotein iHER2 'ikhuthaza ukukhula kweentlobo ezahlukeneyo zomhlaza' kuquka ibele, iqanda, umhlaza wemiphunga nowomhlaza webele.
Indlela efanayo yokuthatha iiseli zomzimba kumguli uze uzifundise indlela yokunyanga iiseli ezinomhlaza iye yasebenza kunyango oluthile lweleukemia.
