I-HIV/AIDS: I-China inikela ingxelo yokunyuka kwamatyala amatsha ali-14%
I-China iye yazisa ukonyuka nge-14% kwinani labemi abaphila ne-HIV ne-AIDS.
Kukho abantu abangaphezu kwama-820 000 abachaphazelekayo kweli lizwe, ngokutsho kwabasebenzi bezempilo.
Kwikota yesibini yonyaka ka-2018 kuphela, kwafunyanwa abantu abangama-40.000.
Uninzi lwamaxhoba amatsha adluliselwa ngeentlobano zesini, ngokungafaniyo noko kwakusenzeka ngaphambili.
Ngokwesiko, iHIV yayisasazeka ngokukhawuleza kwimimandla ethile yaseTshayina ngenxa yokutofelwa kwegazi elinesifo.
Noko ke, inani labantu abanentsholongwane kaGawulayo liye lehla laya kutsho kwaphela, njengoko amagosa ezempilo aseTshayina athetha kwinkomfa eyayiseYunnan.
Noko ke, nyaka ngamnye inani labantu abaneHIV neAIDS eChina liye landa nge-100 000.
Ukusasazeka kwe-HIV ngesondo yingxaki enkulu kuluntu lwama-LGBT e-China.
Ubufanasini babuyekiswa ukuba bubekho emthethweni eChina ngowe-1997, kodwa ukucalulwa kwabantu abangama-LGBT kuqhelekile.
Ngenxa yexabiso eliqhelekileyo, uphando lubonisa ukuba amadoda angama-70 ukusa kuma-90 ekhulwini athandana namafanasini aya kutshata.
Uninzi lwezifo ezosulelayo zibangelwa kukungazikhathaleli kakuhle xa usabelana ngesondo.
Ukususela ngo-2003, urhulumente waseTshayina uye wathembisa ukufikelela kwiyeza ze-HIV kwihlabathi liphela njengenxalenye yomzamo wokulwa nale ngxaki.
