Yintoni i-Global Citizen Festival? Ngaba ikhe yenze nto ukunciphisa ubuhlwempu?
INew York City iza kubamba uMnyhadala weMidlalo yoLuntu owenziwa minyaka le ngoMgqibelo, umnyhadala womculo obonisa iinkwenkwezi ezibalaseleyo, ezenza umsebenzi omangalisayo: ukuphelisa indlala ehlabathini.
Kwisihlandlo sesibhozo kulo nyaka, i-Global Citizen Festival iza kubona amashumi amawaka abantu behlanganisana kwindawo yase-Great Lawn eCentral Park kungekuphela nje ukuze bonwabele imiboniso efana nekaJanet Jackson, uCardi B noShawn Mendes, kodwa kwakhona ukuze bavuselele ulwazi ngenjongo yomnyhadala yokuphelisa ubuhlwempu obugqithisileyo kwihlabathi ngowama-2030.
Umnyhadala weGlobal Citizen, owaqala ngo-2012, lulwandiso lweGlobal Poverty Project, iqela lezomthetho lehlabathi elithemba ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu ngokunyusa inani labantu abancedisa ukulwa nalo.
Ukuze ufumane ukungena simahla kumsitho (ngaphandle kokuba umntu ufuna ukuhlawula ukungena kwe-VIP), ababekho kufuneka benze uthotho lwemisebenzi okanye "izenzo", ezinje ngokuzithandela, ukuthumela i-imeyile kwinkokeli yehlabathi, ukwenza umnxeba okanye nawuphi na omnye umsebenzi wokuphakamisa ulwazi malunga nenjongo yokuphelisa ubuhlwempu.
Yintoni eyenziwe yiGlobal Citizen kwiminyaka eli-12 ngaphambi kokuba ifikelele injongo yayo?
Ingcamango yokuvuza abantu ngemidlalo yaseshashalazini yindlela entle yokubabangela ukuba bafune ukubizwa ukuba benze okuthile okanye nje omnye umzekelo wento esiyibiza ngokuba "kukukhangela" (abantu abacinga ukuba yenza umahluko ngokutyikitya isicelo kwi-intanethi okanye ukuthumela i-tweet?
Ukususela ngo-2011, iGlobal Citizen ithi ibhale ngaphezulu kwe-19 yezigidi "zezabelo" zabaxhasi bayo, ezincede ekufikeleleni kwiinjongo ezahlukeneyo.
Uthi ezi zenzo ziye zanceda ukukhuthaza iinkokheli zehlabathi ukuba zichaze izibophelelo nemigaqo-nkqubo exabisa ngaphezu kwe-USD 37 billion, eya kuba nefuthe kubomi babantu abangaphezu kwe-2.25 bhiliyoni ngowama-2030.
Ekuqaleni kuka-2018, iqela lakhankanya izibophelelo ezingama-390 kunye nezibhengezo ezivela kwizenzo zalo, esele zikhutshiwe okanye ziqokelelwe ubuncinci i-10 yezigidigidi zeedola.
Eli qela liqikelela ukuba ngoku imali ekhuselweyo iye yachaphazela abantu abaphantse babe zizigidi ezingama-649 ehlabathini lonke.
Ezinye zezinto eziphambili ezibandakanyekayo ziquka iThe Power of Nutrition Foundation, umbutho wabatyali mali kunye nabavelisi base-UK, othembisa "ukunceda abantwana bakhule kakuhle kangangoko kunokwenzeka" kwaye uthembisa ukuthumela i-USD 35 yezigidi eRwanda ukunceda ukulwa nokungondleki kweli lizwe emva kokufumana ii-tweets ezingaphezu kwama-4 700 ezivela kwiGlobal Citizens.
"Ngenxa yenkxaso karhulumente wase-UK, abanikeli, oorhulumente besizwe kunye namalungu e-Global Citizens njengawe, singenza ukungalingani kwentlalo ngenxa yokungondleki kube yinxalenye yembali", wathetha njalo u-Ambassador we-The Power of Nutrition uTracey Ullman kwisihlwele ngexesha lomdlalo wobomi eLondon ngo-Apreli 2018.
Eli qela lachaza ukuba emva kwezenzo ezingaphezu kwama-5,000 ezifuna e-UK ukuphucula isondlo somama nomntwana, urhulumente ubhengeze ukuxhasa ngemali iprojekthi, Amandla oNcedo, eya kufikelela kuma-5 ezigidi zabasetyhini nabantwana ngotshintsho lwesondlo.
