Ummeli waseUnited States utyhola iChina ngokuxhaphaza abantu "ngeentengiso zentshumayelo".
Emva kweveki enye iphephandaba laseTshayina liphumeze isibhengezo esinemaphepha amane kwiphephandaba laseMerika, sikhuthaza iingenelo zorhwebo phakathi kwe-US ne-China, ummeli wase-US e-China utyhola i-Beijing ngokusebenzisa amaphephandaba ase-US ukusasaza inkohliso.
UMongameli uDonald Trump wathetha kwi-China Daily pay supplement kwiThe Des Moines Register, iphephandaba elithengiswa kakhulu kwilizwe laseIowa, ngoLwesithathu odlulileyo emva kokumangalela iChina ngokungenelela kunyulo lwe-US Congress ngoNovemba 6, into elahlwa yiChina.
Ityala likaTrump lokuba iPeking izama ukuphazamisa unyulo lwaseUnited States libonisa into abasemagunyeni baseUnited States abayixelele iReuters njengesigaba esitsha senkqubo yaseWashington yokunyusa uxinzelelo eChina.
Nangona kuyinto eqhelekileyo ukuba oorhulumente bamanye amazwe bafake izibhengezo zokukhuthaza urhwebo, iBeijing neWashington ngoku zibandakanyeke kwimfazwe yorhwebo eye yanda, ebone irhafu yokungenisa izinto ezithengiswayo.
Iirhafu zokuziphindezela zase China ekuqaleni kwemfazwe yorhwebo zazenzelwe ukohlwaya abathengisi basemazweni, njengeIowa, abaxhasa iPhathi yeRepublican kaTrump, ngokweengcali zase China naseMelika.
UTery Branstad, ummeli waseUnited States eTshayina nowayesakuba ngumlawuli welizwe laseIowa ixesha elide, umthengisi omkhulu wezolimo eTshayina, wathi iBeijing yayenze umonakalo kubasebenzi baseUnited States, kumafama nakumaqumrhu.
I-China, uBranstad wabhala kwinqaku le-opinion kwi-Des Moines Register ye-The Sunday: "Iphindaphinda ukuxhatshazwa ngokushicilela izibhengezo ze-propaganda kwiphephandaba lethu lasimahla".
"Ekuvakaliseni inkcazelo yawo, urhulumente waseTshayina usebenzisa isithethe saseMerika senkululeko yokuthetha kunye neendaba zasimahla ngokubeka isibhengezo esihlawulelwayo kwiThe Des Moines Register", wabhala watsho uBranstad.
"Ngokwahlukileyo, kwi-kiosk esezitratweni ezisezantsi apha eBeijing, uya kufumana amazwi ambalwa angafaniyo kwaye awuzukufumana nto ibonisa iimbono ezahlukahlukeneyo abemi baseTshayina abanokuba nazo malunga nenkqubela yezoqoqosho yaseTshayina, kuba amajelo eendaba alawulwa yiCPC", wabhala.
Wongezelela wathi "enye yeephephandaba eziphambili eChina yayingafuni ukupapasha" inqaku lakhe, kodwa akazange alichaze igama laloo mpapasho.
