Umqambi weWebhu yeHlabathi Jikelele uceba ukwenza i-Intanethi entsha ukuze akhuphisane noGoogle noFacebook
UTim Berners-Lee, umqambi wewebhu, usungula inkampani entsha ezama ukukhuphisana neFacebook, Amazon neGoogle.
Iprojekthi yokugqibela yeengcali zeteknoloji, i-Inrupt, yinkampani esekwe kwiqonga lomthombo ovulekileyo uSolide kaBerners-Lee.
Iqonga leSolid livumela abasebenzisi ukuba bakhethe ukuba bagcinwa phi iinkcukacha zabo kwaye ngoobani abanokufikelela kulwazi oluthile.
Kudliwano-ndlebe olukhethekileyo neFast Company, uBerners-Lee waqhula esithi injongo efihlakeleyo ye-Inrupt "yayikukulawula ihlabathi".
"Kufuneka siyenze ngoku", watsho ngoshishino olutsha.
"Eli lixesha lembali".
Isicelo sisebenzisa itekhnoloji yeqonga leSolid ukuvumela abasebenzisi ukuba benze eyabo "indawo yokugcina idatha ekwi-intanethi" okanye i-POD.
Inokuqulatha uluhlu lwabafowunelwa, uluhlu lwemisebenzi engapheliyo, ikhalenda, ithala lomculo kunye nezinye izixhobo zobuqu nezomsebenzi.
I-Google Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, iSlack neSpotify. Zonke ziyafumaneka kwisikhangeli esinye ngexesha elinye.
Into ekhethekileyo ngendawo yokugcina idatha kwi-intanethi kukuba umsebenzisi nguye ogqiba ukuba ngubani onokuthi afumane ulwazi oluthile.
Le nkampani ibiza oku ngokuthi "kukomeleza umntu ngokusebenzisa idatha".
Ingcamango yeInrupt, ngokutsho kwe-CEO yenkampani, uJohn Bruce, kukuba inkampani ifake izixhobo ezifanelekileyo, iinkqubo kunye nezakhono ukuze iqonga leSolid lifumaneke kuwo wonke umntu.
Inkampani ngoku ibandakanya uBerners-Lee, uBruce, iqonga lokhuseleko elifunyenwe yi-IBM, abanye abaphuhlisi abasebenza ngokusemthethweni abaqeshelwe ukusebenza kule projekthi kunye noluntu lwabaqulunqi abazithandela.
Ukuqala kule veki, abaphuhlisi bezobuchwephesha kwihlabathi liphela baya kuba nakho ukudala ezonaapps zabo zithe kratya besebenzisa izixhobo ezikhoyo kwiwebhusayithi ye-Inrupt.
UBerners-Lee wathi akukho namnye kwiqela lakhe othetha ne "Facebook neGoogle malunga nokuba kufuneka kungeniswe utshintsho olukhulu apho zonke iimodeli zeshishini ziphela ngokupheleleyo ngobusuku obunye.
"Asizukucela imvume".
Kwiphepha likaMgqibelo kwiMedium, uBerners-Lee wabhala ukuba umsebenzi weInrupt kukubonelela ngamandla orhwebo kunye ne-ecosystem yokunceda ukukhusela ukuthembeka kunye nomgangatho wewebhu entsha ebandakanyiweyo kwiqonga leSolid.
Ngowe-1994, uBerners-Lee watshintsha i-Intanethi xa waseka i-World Wide Web Consortium kwi-MIT.
Kwiinyanga ezimbalwa ezidlulileyo, uBerners-Lee uye waba lilizwi elinamandla kwingxoxo-mpikiswano malunga nokungathathi hlangothi kwewebhu.
Nokuba ngexesha lokukhutshwa kwe-Inrupt, uBerners-Lee uya kuqhubeka engumseki kunye nomlawuli we-World Wide Web Consortium, i-World Wide Web Foundation kunye ne-Open Data Institute.
"Ndiqinisekile ukuba eli lixesha elitsha lewebhu", wongezelela uBerners-Lee.
