U-Lieutenant Colonel kunye no-Reverend Bernard Vann wafumana ibhaso ngoSeptemba 29, 1918 ngokuhlasela eBellenglise naseLehaucourt.
Nangona kunjalo, wadutyulwa ngumdubuli emva kweentsuku ezine kwaye akazange azi ukuba uzuze elona wonga libalulekileyo lomkhosi waseBritane.
Abazukulwana bakhe ababini bafumana ilitye lesikhumbuzo kumngcelele ngoMgqibelo eRushden, eNorthamptonshire.
Omnye wabazukulwana bakhe, uMichael Vann, wathi "yayingumfuziselo omhle" ukuba ilitye lesikhumbuzo lavela kwiminyaka eyi-100 emva kokuba utatomkhulu wakhe enikwe umvuzo.
Ngokutsho kweThe London Gazette, ngoSeptemba 29, 1918, uLieutenant Colonel Vann wakhokela ibutho lakhe kwi-St-Quentin Canal "ngokusebenzisa inkungu eninzi kwaye phantsi komlilo omkhulu weembumbulu kunye ne-metal gun".
Kamva wabaleka waya kumgca wokudubula kwaye, "ngobungqina obugqithisileyo" wenza ukuba umgca uqhubele phambili ngaphambi kokuba aziphose phezu kompu ngesandla esinye kwaye ashiye amalungu amathathu e-detachment emangalisiwe.
Lo kaLt. Col. wabulawa ngumdubuli waseJamani ngo-Oktobha 4, 1918, kwinyanga nje enye ngaphambi kokuba imfazwe iphele.
UMichael Vann (72) wathi izenzo zikayisemkhulu wakhe yayizizinto awayengenakuze akwazi ukuzenza, nto leyo ekwenza uthobeke.
