UTom Daley wayeziva phantsi malunga nesini
Umgadi weOlimpiki uTom Daley uthi wakhula eziva ephantsi kwabanye abantu ngenxa yesini sakhe, kodwa oko kwamnika inkuthazo yokuphumelela.
Lo mdlali oneminyaka engama-24 ubudala uthi akazange aqonde de waya kwisikolo samabanga aphakamileyo ukuba ayinguye wonke umntu onjengaye.
Kwi-Desert Island Discs yeRadio 4, eyayinomdla kaLauren Laverne, wathi uthetha ngamalungelo abantu abathandanayo ukuze anike abanye abantu ithemba.
Kwakhona wathi ukuba ngutata kuye kwabangela ukuba angakuboni ukubaluleka kokuphumelela kwiiOlimpiki.
Umninimzi osoloko ethetha ngale nkqubo, uKirsty Young, uye wathatha iinyanga ezimbalwa engaphangeli ngenxa yokugula.
UDaley, owabonakala njengonxeleko kwinkqubo yokuqala kaLaverne, wathi wayeziva "engaphantsi" kwabanye kuba "wayengamkelekanga ekuhlaleni njengamakhwenkwe namantombazana".
Wathi: "Namhlanje, iimvakalelo zokungaphantsi nokungafani, zizinto zokwenene ezindinika amandla namandla okuphumelela".
Wayefuna ukubonisa ukuba "wayengumntu", watsho, ukuze angadumali nabani na xa ekugqibeleni efumanisa ngesini sakhe.
Lo mdlali weembasa ezimbini zeOlimpiki uye waba ngumkhuthazi ophezulu we-LGBT kwaye wasebenzisa umfanekiso wakhe kwiiMidlalo ze-Commonwealth kulo nyaka e-Australia ukucela amazwe amaninzi ukuba athathe ubufanasini njengento engekho mthethweni.
Wathi wathetha kuba wayeziva enethamsanqa kuba wayekwazi ukuphila ubomi bakhe ngokuvulekileyo ngaphandle kweziphumo, yaye wayefuna ukunika abanye abantu "ithemba".
Umdlali webhola ekhatywayo wehlabathi wachaza ukuba wayethandana nendoda, umlawuli wefilimu waseMelika, uDustin Lance Black, owazifumana ngo-2013, "wandithabatha ndothuka".
Kunyaka ophelileyo, uDaley watshata nomntu owaphumelela iOscar, owayemdala kunaye ngeminyaka engama-20, kodwa uthi umehluko weminyaka awuzange ube yingxaki.
Uthi xa uselula (wathatha inxaxheba kwiiOlimpiki zakhe zokuqala xa wayeneminyaka eli-14 ubudala waza uyise wafa ngumhlaza kwiminyaka emithathu kamva), kunzima ukufumana umntu oneminyaka efanayo oye wafumana izinto ezifanayo.
Esi sibini saba ngabazali ngoJuni wonyana ogama linguRobert Ray Black-Daley. Ngokutsho kukaDaley, "lonke ithemba lakhe" litshintshile.
"Ukuba ububuze kunyaka ophelileyo, yonke into endiyifunayo kukuphumelela igolide yeOlimpiki", watsho.
"Kukho izinto ezibaluleke ngakumbi kunemali yegolide kwiiOlimpiki.
Igolide yam yeOlimpiki nguRobbie".
Unyana wakhe ubizwa ngokuba nguyise, uRobert, owafa ngo-2011, eneminyaka engama-40 ubudala ngenxa yomhlaza wengqondo.
NgokukaDaley, uyise akazange amkele ukuba wayeza kufa kwaye enye yezinto zokugqibela awazicelayo yayikukuba sele benayo na amatikiti eLondon 2012 kuba wayefuna ukuba kumqolo wokuqala.
"Andinakumxelela ukuba 'Tata, awuzukuba semgceni wokuqala'", watsho.
"Njengoko ndambamba ngesandla, wayeka ukuphefumla kwaye kwakungekho de kwaba ngoku, ukuba wayesele efile, ukuba ekugqibeleni ndamkela ukuba wayengekho ongenakoyiswa", watsho.
Kunyaka olandelayo, uDaley wakhuphisana kwiiOlimpiki zowama-2012 waza waphumelela ibronzi.
"Ndandisazi ukuba yinto endandiyiphupha ubomi bam bonke - ukujikela phambi kwesihlwele ekhaya kwiiOlimpiki. Kwakungekho mvakalelo ibhetele", watsho.
Kwakhona waphefumlela ukhetho lweengoma zakhe zokuqala (Proud kaHeather Small), awayeyimamele ngexesha lokulungiselela iMidlalo yeOlimpiki kwaye eyayisambeka isikhumba senkukhu.
