Inqanawa entsha yemfazwe yaseJamani, iphinde yabekelwa elinye ixesha
I-frigate entsha yoMkhosi waseJamani yayifanele ukuba yagqitywa ngo-2014 ukuze ithathe indawo yeenqanawa ezindala zemfazwe zexesha leMfazwe ebandayo, kodwa ayizukwenza oko, ubuncinci, kude kube ngunyaka olandelayo ngenxa yeenkqubo ezingasebenziyo kunye nokunyuka kweendleko, ngokweendaba zasekuhlaleni.
Ukugqitywa kwe Rheinland-Pfalz, inqanawa ephambili yeefregates ezintsha zodidi lweBaden-Württemberg, iye yahlehliswa de kube sisiqingatha sokuqala sonyaka ka-2019, ngokwephephandaba iDie Zeit, ecaphula isithethi somkhosi.
Inqanawa ibifanele ukuba yajoyina uMkhosi ngo-2014, kodwa iingxaki ezalandelayo kulwakhiwo ziphawule ixesha lokugqibela le projekthi inqwenelekayo.
Iinqanawa ezine zodidi lweBaden-Württemberg ezathunyelwa ngumkhosi wamanzi ngo-2007 ziya kuthatha indawo yeefrakthi zakudala zodidi lweBremen.
Kucingelwa ukuba iya kubandakanya umpu onamandla, iseti ye-anti-aircraft kunye ne-anti-ship missiles, kunye netekhnoloji yokulwa nezenzo ezifihlakeleyo, ezinje ngerabha encinci, i-infrared kunye ne-acoustic signatures.
Ezinye iimpawu ezibalaseleyo zibandakanya amaxesha amade phakathi kokugcinwa: kufanele ukuba kunokwenzeka ukusebenzisa iifregates ezintsha ukuya kuthi ga kwiminyaka emibini ngaphandle kokuhamba kwizibuko lasekhaya.
Nangona kunjalo, ezi zityhafiselo ziqhubekayo zithetha ukuba iinqanawa eziphambili, ezazijongwe ukuba zinokuqhayisa eJamani njengamandla amakhulu phesheya, ziya kuba sele zingaphelelwa lixesha xa zingena ekusebenzeni, ngokweDie Zeit.
I-frigate engathandekiyo i-F125 sele yenze iindaba kunyaka ophelileyo, xa i-Army yaseJamani yayikhaba inqanawa yaza yayibuyisela kwi-dresdner Blohm & Voss eHamburg.
Yayikokokuqala ukuba uMkhosi weMfazwe ubuyisele inqanawa kumakhi emva kokuba inikezelwe.
Zimbalwa iinkcukacha ezaziwayo ngezizathu zokuba ibuyiselwe, kodwa amajelo eendaba aseJamani acaphula "iziphene eziphathekayo nezobuchwephesha" zenqanawa ezazinokwenza ukuba ingasebenzi ukuba isetyenziswe kwimisebenzi yokulwa.
Iingxaki zobugcisa zibalulekile, kuba malunga nabanxweme abali-120, isiqingatha sabasebenzi abafunekayo kwiifregates zangaphambili zeklasi yaseBremen, basebenza kwiinqanawa zeklasi yaseBaden-Württemberg.
Ukongeza, kuye kwaziwa ukuba ubunzima benqanawa bungaphezulu, nto leyo enciphisa ukusebenza kwayo kwaye inqanda amandla oMkhosi wokongeza ukuphuculwa kwexesha elizayo.
Kucingelwa ukuba i Rheinland-Pfalz, yeetoni ezingama-7.000, iya kuba nobunzima obuphindwe kabini kunenqanawa zodidi olufanayo ezisetyenziswa ngamaJamani ngexesha leMfazwe yesibini yeHlabathi.
Ngaphandle kwezinto ezinesiphene, iindleko zeprojekthi, eziquka uqeqesho lwabasebenzi, nazo ziqala ukuba yingxaki.
Kuqikelelwa ukuba iye yafikelela kwii-euro eziziibhiliyoni eziyi-3.100 (ii-dollar eziziibhiliyoni eziyi-3.600) ukusuka kwibhajethi yokuqala ye-euro eziziibhiliyoni eziyi-2.2.
Iingxaki zeefregates ezintsha ziye zaba ngumcimbi obaluleke ngokukodwa, ukuba kuthathelwa ingqalelo izilumkiso zamva nje ezibonisa ukuba amandla omkhosi waselwandle waseJamani ayanyamalala.
Kulo nyaka, uHans-Peter Bartels, intloko yekomiti yokhuselo yePalamente yaseJamani, uvumile ukuba uMkhosi weMfazwe uphelelwa zizikhephe ezinokusetyenziswa.
Igosa lathi imeko iye yaba mandundu ngokuhamba kwexesha kuba iinqanawa ezindala zaphela zingasasetyenziswa, kodwa akukho nanye entsha enikezelweyo njengendawo yokutshintsha.
Uxolise ukuba akukho nanye kwiifregates zeBaden-Württemberg-class ezingenako ukujoyina iArmada.
