I-Brexit: I-UK  iya kuhlala izisola ngokulahlekelwa ngabavelisi bezithuthi
I-UK iya kuhlala izisola, ukuba ilahlekelwa sisikhundla sayo njengenkokeli yehlabathi kwimveliso emva kwe-Brexit, ngokutsho kuka-Greg Clark, uNobhala wezezoqoqosho.
Wongeze wathi "kwakukhathaza" ukuba isiseko sikaToyota e-UK sathi kwi-BBC ukuba, ukuba i-UK yayishiya i-European Union ngaphandle kokufikelela kwisivumelwano, yayiza kuyeka okwethutyana ukuvelisa kumzi-mveliso waseBurnaston, kufuphi neDerby.
"Kufuneka sifikelele kwisivumelwano", watsho uClark.
Le mveliso yaseJapan ithe ifuthe lokulibaziseka kwemida kwimeko yeBrexit engenasivumelwano linokubangela ukulahleka kwemisebenzi.
Isityalo saseBurnaston, esenza iimodeli zeAuris neAvensis zikaToyota, sivelise iimoto ezili-150.000 kunyaka ophelileyo, apho ama-90% athunyelwa kwamanye amazwe kwi-European Union.
"Into endicinga ngayo kukuba, ukuba iUK iyashiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano ekupheleni kuka-Matshi, imveliso iya kuyeka kumzi-mveliso wethu", utshilo uMarvin Cooke, oyintloko yolawulo lweToyota eBurnaston.
Ukuphuma kwi-EU kungekho sivumelwano malunga nendlela urhwebo oluzakusebenza ngayo namanye amazwe e-EU kuye kwavusa uloyiko lwabanye abenzi beemoto base-UK, abanjengoHonda, BMW, Jaguar kunye neLand Rover.
Umzekelo, iBMW ithi izakuvala isityalo seMini eOxford kwinyanga enye emva kweBrexit.
Ezona zinto zixhalabisayo zinxulumene noko abavelisi bakujonga njengeengozi kumgca wemveliso kwimeko yeBrexit engenasivumelwano.
Umgca wemveliso weToyota wenziwa kwisiseko ngexesha elifanelekileyo, kunye namalungu afika rhoqo ngemizuzu engama-37 evela kubathengisi base-UK kunye ne-European Union yokwenziwa kweemoto.
Ukuba iUnited Kingdom iyashiya i-European Union ingakhange ifikelele kwisivumelwano ngoMatshi 29, kusenokwenzeka ukuba kubekho iziphazamiso emdeni, icinga ukuba oku kunokubangela ukulibaziseka nokunqongophala kwezinto.
Bekungayi kuba lula ukuba iToyota igcine uluhlu lwezinto ngaphezu kosuku olunye kwisityalo saseDerbyshire, ngokwenkampani, kwaye kufuneka imise imveliso ngenxa yoko.
UClark uthi isicwangciso sikaTheresa May seChequers sobudlelwane bexesha elizayo ne-EU 'sihlolwe ngokuchanekileyo ukuze siphephe ezi ngqesho zemida'.
Sifuna ukufumana esona sivumelwano silungileyo esiya kusivumela, njengoko nditshoyo, singavuyeli nje impumelelo yethu kodwa sisebenzise eli thuba, utshilo kwi-BBC Radio 4's Today show.
Uvavanyo hayi kuphela oluvela eToyota, kodwa nolunye oluvela kwabanye abavelisi, lubonisa ukuba kufuneka sikwazi ukuqhubeka neseti yemigca yemveliso ephumelelayo
UToyota akakwazi ukuqinisekisa ukuba imveliso iza kumiswa ixesha elingakanani, kodwa, kwixesha elide, ulumkise ukuba iindleko ezongeziweyo ziya kunciphisa ukhuphiswano lwesityalo kwaye zinokubangela ukulahleka kwemisebenzi.
UPeter Tsouvallaris, osebenze eBurnaston iminyaka engama-24 nolilungu lomququzeleli we-UNITE the Union kwisityalo, uthe amalungu aqalisa ukuba nexhala kakhulu ngale meko: "Ngokwamava, xa ezi zithuba zingasekho, azibuyi".
