Intlanganiso kaDonald Trump eyayilindelwe kakhulu kunye nosekela-mtshutshisi jikelele uRod Rosenstein inokuhlehliswa ngeveki njengoko umlo malunga nomntu otyunjwe kwinkundla ephakamileyo, uBrett Kavanaugh uqhubeka, kwiingxelo ezivela kwiNdlu ye-White House ngeCawa.
URosenstein ukhokela umsebenzi weNgcali yeNgxelo eziZodwa uRobert Mueller, ophanda ngotshintsho lwaseRashiya kunyulo, unxibelelwano phakathi kweRashiya noncedo lukaTrump kunye nokungakwazi ukufikelela emthethweni ngumongameli.
Ukuba uTrump uya kumgxotha okanye hayi igosa elisezantsi lezomthetho kwaye ubeke emngciphekweni ukuzimela kukaMueller, kuye kwafaka iindudumo eWashington kangangeenyanga.
Kule nyanga, iNew York Times yachaza ukuba uRosenstein wayexubusha ngokufaka umbhobho ukuze abhale iintetho zakhe noTrump, kwanokuxothwa kukaMongameli ngeSichilimbela-25.
URosenstein wakhanyela ukuba akukho nto ayithethayo.
Kodwa ngoMvulo odlulileyo waya e-White House phakathi kweengxelo zokuba uza kurhoxa.
Nangona kunjalo, kwabhengezwa ngoLwesine intlanganiso noTrump, eyayikwiZizwe eziManyeneyo eNew York.
UTrump uthe  angafuna  ukumkhupha uRosenstein, kodwa wayeka ukudibana ukuze aphephe ukudibana nentlanganiso yeKomiti yezomthetho yeSenate apho uKavanaugh kunye nomnye wabafazi abamtyhola ngokuziphatha kakubi ngokwesondo, uGqr. Christine Blasey Ford, bangqina.
NgoLwesihlanu, uTrump wayalela ukuba i-FBI iphando ngeveki malunga nezityholo ezenziwa nguKavanaugh, nto leyo eyalandela ukuvotelwa kweSenate.
Intatheli kaTrump uSarah Sanders, wavela kwiFox News ngeCawa.
Xa ebuzwa ngentlanganiso yakhe noRosenstein, waphendula wathi: Akukho mhla ubekiweyo okwangoku, isenokuba kule veki, nangona isenokulibaziseka iveki enye ngenxa yemicimbi yenkundla ephakamileyo.
Kodwa siza kubona. Ndihlala ndifuna ukugcina amaphephandaba enolwazi.
