USanders uthe iintlanganiso zokwazisa ziya kuqhubeka, kodwa ukuba abeendaba banethuba lokubuza umongameli waseUnited States ngqo, kungcono kakhulu kunokuthetha nam.
Sizama ukwenza oku rhoqo, nisibonile sisenza oku kaninzi kwezi veki zidlulileyo kwaye siza kuthatha indawo yeengxoxo zengcaciso-magama xa ninokuthetha nomongameli waseUnited States.
UTrump uphendula imibuzo xa ephuma e-White House okanye ethatha inxaxheba kwiiseshoni ezivulekileyo okanye iintlanganiso noonondaba kunye nezikhulu ezindwendwele ngokusemthethweni.
Iinqwelo zenkqubo nganye aziqhelekanga.
Kule veki eNew York, umongameli usenokuba ubonise isizathu, emva kokuvela ngokungacwangciswanga, yaye ngamanye amaxesha, ngendlela engaqhelekanga phambi kwamaphephandaba ahlanganiseneyo.
UMphathiswa Wezempilo Ubhalela Abasebenzi Base-EU Be-Scotland Health Service Ngenxa Yokoyika I-Brexit
UNobhala wezeMpilo ubhalele abasebenzi base-EU abasebenza kwi-Scottish National Health Service ukuvakalisa umbulelo welizwe kwaye unqwenela ukuba baqhubeke emva kweBrexit.
UJeane Freeman, olilungu lePalamente yaseScotland, wathumela ileta kwiinyanga ezingaphantsi kwezintandathu ngaphambi kokuba iUnited Kingdom iphume kwi-EU.
Urhulumente waseScotland sele ezibophelele ekuhlawuleni iindleko zezicelo zokubekwa kwindawo yokuhlala kubemi base-EU abasebenza kwiinkonzo zikarhulumente.
Kwileta yakhe, uFreeman wabhala oku kulandelayo: Ebudeni behlobo, uthethathethwano phakathi kwe-UK ne-EU malunga nokuphuma luye lwaqhubeka, kwaye yonke into ibonakala isendleleni eya kwizigqibo ezilindelekileyo kule mpela.
Kodwa urhulumente wase-UK naye uqalile ukulungiselela imeko engenakwenzeka ngaphandle kwesivumelwano.
Ndiyazi ukuba la ngamaxesha anzima kuni nonke.
Ngoko ke, ndifuna ukuphinda ndivakalise ukuba ndiyayixabisa kakhulu igalelo labasebenzi bam, nokuba ngabaluphi na uhlanga.
Amaqabane ethu e-EU, nangaphaya, azisa amava axabisekileyo nezakhono ezomeleza ziphucule umsebenzi wenkonzo yezempilo, ngelixa kusetyenziswa izigulana noluntu esizinyamekelayo.
Kakade ke, iSkotlani likhaya lenu yaye sifuna nihlale apha.
