Umqeqeshi welizwe laseTennessee, uRod Reed, uxelele abeendaba ukuba ukonzakala kwenzeka ngaphambi nje kwesiqingatha.
"Waya kumgca webhanti waza wawa apho", watsho uReed.
Abaqeqeshi nabasebenzi bezonyango banika uAbercrombie ioksijini kwibhanti ngaphambi kokuba bamfake ebhedini baze bamthabathe ukuze benze iimvavanyo ezingakumbi.
Igosa laseTennessee State lazise uChris Harris, weWSMV eNashville, eTennessee, ukuba uAbercrombie uphumile kwigumbi lokusebenza kwiziko lezonyango laseVanderbilt.
UHarris wongeze wathi "akukho lwazi lungako malunga nohlobo okanye ubungakanani bonzakele" kwaye iTennessee State iyaphanda ukuba wenzeke nini.
Lixesha lokuqala lomnyaka wesibini ka-Abercrombie kunye ne-Tennessee State emva kokubhalisa evela e-Illinois.
Wayegqibezele ukubetha izibane ezintlanu ngoMgqibelo ngaphambi kokuba emke kumdlalo, oko kwenza ukuba abe li-18 lilonke kweli xesha.
Abathengi bamanye amazwe baya kuhlawula irhafu ephezulu yesitampu xa bethenga ipropathi e-UK
Abathengi bamanye amazwe baya kuhlawulwa irhafu ephezulu yokuthengisa xa bethenga ipropathi e-UK ngemali eyongezelelweyo esetyenziselwa ukunceda abantu abangenamakhaya phantsi kwecebo elitsha leqela leT Conservative.
Esi senzo siya kuthintela impumelelo yentshukumo kaCorbyn yokutsala abavoti abancinci.
Ukunyuka kwirhafu yesitampu kuya kuhlawuliswa abo bangahlawuli rhafu e-UK.
IHansenda inethemba lokufumana ukuya kuthi ga kwi-120 yezigidi zeedola ngonyaka ukunceda abantu abangenamakhaya.
Abathengi bamanye amazwe kulindeleke ukuba bahlawule irhafu ephezulu xa bethenga izindlu e-UK kwaye loo mali iza kusetyenziswa ukunceda abantu abangenamakhaya, inyathelo eliza kubhengezwa nguTheresa May namhlanje.
Esi senzo sijongwa njengokuzama ukuthintela impumelelo yentshukumo kaJeremy Corbyn yokutsala abavoti abancinci ngezithembiso zokubonelela ngezindlu ezifikelelekayo eziza kuchaphazela umvuzo ophezulu.
Ukunyuka kwerhafu yesitampu kuya kuhlawuliswa abo bantu kunye neenkampani ezingahlawuli rhafu e-UK; le mali iya kubhatala isenzo sikarhulumente sokulwa namanani abantu abangenamakhaya.
Umthwalo omkhulu, oza kongezwa kwirhafu yangoku yesitampu, kuquka amanqanaba aphezulu angeniswe kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo kwizindlu zesibini nakwizindlu ezithengiswayo, unokuba ngama-3%.
I-Hazenda ilindele ukufumana ukuya kuthi ga kwi-120 yezigidi zeedola ngonyaka.
Kuqikelelwa ukuba i-13% yepropathi entsha eLondon inabantu abangengabo baseBritane, nto leyo inyusa amaxabiso kwaye yenza kube nzima kubathengi abatsha ukuba bavule indlela yabo kwinqanaba lepropathi.
Iindawo ezininzi zelizwe ezifumileyo, ingakumbi ikomkhulu, ziye zaba 'ziidolophu ezingekhoyo' ngenxa yenani elikhulu labathengi bamanye amazwe abachitha ixesha labo elininzi ngaphandle kwelizwe.
Eli nyathelo liza emva kweeveki uBoris Johnson ecela ukuncitshiswa kwerhafu yesitampu ukunceda ulutsha lube nekhaya lokuqala.
Watyhola abakhi abakhulu ngokugcina amaxabiso ezindlu ephakamileyo ngokuthenga umhlaba ngokukhawuleza kwaye ungayisebenzisi, kwaye wabongoza uMay ukuba ashenxise iirhafu kwizindlu ezifikelelekayo ukulungisa i "disaster real estate" yaseBritane.
UCorbyn ubhengeze uthotho lweenguqu ezifanelekileyo kwizindlu, njengokulawula irente nokupheliswa kokukhutshwa kwabantu ngaphandle kwetyala.
Ufuna ukunika amalungelo amaninzi oomasipala ukwakha amakhaya amatsha.
UMay wathi: "Kulo nyaka uphelileyo ndathi ndiza kunikezela ixesha lam ekubuyiseleni iphupha laseBritani: ubomi bufanele bube ngcono kwisizukulwana ngasinye.
Oko kuthetha ukulungisa imarike yethu yokuthengiswa kwezindlu.
IBritani iya kuhlala ivulelekile kuye nabani na ofuna ukuhlala, ukusebenza nokwenza ubomi bakhe apha.
Nangona kunjalo, akunakulungiswa ukuba kulula kubantu abangekho e-UK, kunye neenkampani ezisekwe phesheya, ukuthenga amakhaya xa kuthelekiswa nabemi base-UK abasebenza nzima.
Kubantu abaninzi kakhulu, iphupha lokuba nekhaya likhulu kakhulu kwaye ukungabi namakhaya kwenza ukuba kube yinto yokwenene.
