Iinyikima Neetsunami EIndonesia
Ubuncinane abantu abangama-384 babulawa yinyikima enkulu kunye netsunami eyahlasela isixeko saseIndonesia iPalu ngoLwesihlanu, ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni.
Ngenxa yokuba unxibelelwano luvaliwe, amaqela anceda abantu abakwimeko enzima akakwazi ukufumana inkcazelo kwiDonggala Regency, ummandla okumantla ePalu okufutshane nendawo eyayibetheleke kuyo le nyikima.
EPalu, abantu abangaphezu kwe-16 000 baye bagxothwa emva kwentlekele.
Apha ngezantsi kukho ezinye iinkcukacha ezibalulekileyo malunga nePalu neDonggala, kwisiqithi saseCèlebes:
IPalu likomkhulu lePhondo laseCèlebes Central, libekwe ekupheleni kwebhulorho emxinwa kunxweme olusentshona lwesiqithi saseCèlebes, elinabantu abamalunga nama-379,800 ngonyaka ka-2017.
Esi sixeko sasigubha iminyaka engama-40 sisandul' ukuzalwa xa kwabakho inyikima kunye netsunami.
I-Donggala yi-regency ehlala ngaphezu kweekhilomitha ezingama-300 kunxweme olusenyakatho-ntshona yesiqithi saseCèlebes.
I-regency, ummandla wolawulo ophantsi kwiphondo, yayinabemi abamalunga nama-299 200 abantu ngonyaka ka-2017.
Ukurhweba ngokuloba kunye nezolimo ziintsika zoqoqosho kwiphondo laseCelebes Central, ngakumbi kwingingqi engaselunxwemeni yaseDonggala.
Ukuxhaphaza imigodi ye-nickel nayo ibalulekile kwiphondo, kodwa igxile, ikakhulu, eMorowali, kunxweme olukumnye umda weCèlebes.
IPalu neDonggala ziye zathwaxwa ziitsunami ezininzi kwiminyaka eli-100 edluleyo, ngokutsho kweArhente Yokunciphisa Iintlekele yaseIndonesia.
Ngowe-1938, itsunami yabulala abantu abangaphezu kwama-200 yaza yatshabalalisa amakhulu ezindlu eDonggala.
Ngowe-1996 kwabakho itsunami kwintshona yeDonggala eyabulala abantu abasithoba.
I-Indonesia ikwiPacific Ring of Fire yaye idla ngokutshatyalaliswa ziinyikima.
Apha ngezantsi kudweliswe iinyikima ezinkulu kunye neetsunami zeminyaka yakutshanje:
2004: NgoDisemba 26, inyikima enkulu kunxweme olusentshona kwiphondo laseIndonesia iAce, kumantla eSumatra, yabangela itsunami eyachaphazela amazwe ali-14 yaza yabulala abantu abangama-226,000 kunxweme loLwandlekazi lwaseIndiya, abangaphezu kwesiqingatha sabo eAceh.
Ngo-2005: Kwabakho inyikima enkulu kunxweme olusentshona yeSumatra ekupheleni kukaMatshi nasekuqaleni kuka-Aprili.
Amawaka abantu bafa kwisiqithi saseNias, kunxweme lwaseSumatra.
Ngo-2006: Inyikima enkulu enobungakanani be-6.8 yahlasela isiqithi esisezantsi saseJava, esona siqithi sinabantu abaninzi eIndonesia, yaza yabangela itsunami eyabulala abantu abamalunga nabayi-700.
Ngo-2009: Inyikima enkulu enobungakanani be-7.6 yahlasela idolophu yasePadang, ikomkhulu lephondo laseNtshona Sumatra.
Kwafa abantu abangaphezu kwe-1 100.
Ngo-2010: Inyikima enkulu enkulu eyabangela itsunami enkulu eyayingangeemitha eziyi-10 yashiya abantu abayi-300 befile.
Ngo-2016: Inyikima encinane yahlasela iPidie Jaya eAceh yaza yabangela intshabalalo nentlungu njengoko abantu babekhumbula indlela eyatshabalala ngayo yinyikima netsunami eyatshabalalisa abantu abaninzi ngo-2004.
Kuloo mini, akuzange kubekho tsunami, kodwa abantu abangaphezu kwe-100 bafa ngenxa yezakhiwo ezidilikileyo.
Ngo-2018: Iinyikima ezinkulu zenzeka kwisiqithi saseIndonesia esingummandla weholide iLombok, zabulala abantu abangaphezu kwe-500, abaninzi babo kumantla esiqithi.
Le nyikima yatshabalalisa amawaka ezakhiwo yaza yashiya amawaka abakhenkethi bevalelwe.
Unyana kaSarah Palin ubanjwe ngezityholo zogonyamelo lwasekhaya
UTrack Palin, unyana omdala wombusi waseAlaska nowayekade engumbongameli uSarah Palin, ubanjwe ngezityholo zokubetha.
UPalin, oneminyaka engama-29 ubudala, waseWasilla, eAlaska, wabanjwa ngokumangalelwa ngobundlobongela basekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo yobundlobongela basekhaya nokumelana nokuvalelwa, ngokwengxelo epapashwe ngoMgqibelo yiAlaska State Troopers.
Ngokwengxelo yamapolisa, xa umntu awayemazi wazama ukufowunela amapolisa ukuze axele ngezityholo ezenziwayo, wawunika ifowuni.
UPalin ubanjwe kwiziko lokuvalela elingenammiselo laseMat-Su, apho agcinwe khona ngebheyile engakhange ibekwe phantsi kwe-USD 500, ngokutsho kweKTUU.
Uvele enkundleni ngoMgqibelo, xa wathi "akanatyala, ngokuqinisekileyo" xa ebuzwa ukuba uvakalisa njani, ngokutsho kwale nqwelomoya.
UPalin ujongene nezityholo ezintathu zeClass A, nto leyo ethetha ukuba angaya entolongweni ukuya kutsho kunyaka omnye aze ahlawule isohlwayo esifikelela kwi-250,000 USD.
Ukwatyholwa ngokwaphula umthetho weClass B, onetyala lokuvalelwa entolongweni usuku olunye kunye nokuhlawuliswa i-USD 2,000.
Ayingeloxesha lokuqala ukuba kuvele izityholo zolwaphulo-mthetho nxamnye noPalin.
NgoDisemba 2017 watyholwa ngokurhweba uyise, uTodd Palin.
Unina, uSarah Palin, wabiza amapolisa ukuba axele ngokuhlaselwa.
Ngoku eli tyala lisezandleni zeNkundla Yamajoni Omkhosi WaseAlaska.
NgoJanuwari 2016 watyholwa ngokuhlaselwa ekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo yesenzo sobundlobongela basekhaya kunye nokufumana isixhobo xa wayenxilile ngokunxulumene nesiganeko.
Iqabane lakhe lathi lambetha ebusweni.
Ngowe-2016, uSarah Palin wagxekwa ngamaqela omkhosi omdala ngokudibanisa ukuziphatha kobundlobongela konyana wakhe ne-post-traumatic stress disorder evela kwinkonzo yakhe e-Iraq.
Inyikima Netsunami EIndonesia - Amakhulu Abulawa
