Le nyikima yomhlaba enobungakanani be-7.5 yabangela itsunami yaza yatshabalalisa amawaka ezindlu.
Umbane nonxibelelwano alusebenzi yaye inani labantu abafayo kulindeleke ukuba linyuke kwiintsuku ezizayo.
Le nyikima yenzeke kunxweme lwaseCelebes Central, kumntla-mpuma weJakarta, ikomkhulu laseIndonesia.
Kwiintanethi zentlalo, abantu abaninzi baye bafumana iividiyo ezibonisa ixesha lokuwa.
