Abashushisi basemthethweni bafuna isigwebo sokufa esikhethekileyo kumntu osolwa ngokuhlasela kwamaphekula eNew York
Abashushisi baseNew York bafuna isigwebo sokufa kuSayfullo Saipov, oyena mntu usolwa ngokuhlasela kwamaphekula eNew York okwabangela ukuba kufe abantu abasibhozo: isigwebo esingaqhelekanga esingazange senziwe kweli lizwe ngenxa yetyala likarhulumente ukususela ngowe-1953.
USaipov, oneminyaka engama-30 ubudala, kuthiwa wasebenzisa ilori eqeshwe yiHome Depot ukuze aqhube uhlaselo kwindawo yokuhamba ngebhayisekile kwiWest Side Highway, eLower Manhattan waza wagqogqa abakhweli beebhayisekile nohambo lwabo ngo-Oktobha.
Ukuze kuqinisekiswe isigwebo sokufa, abatshutshisi kufuneka babonise ukuba uSaipov wabulala onke amaxhoba asibhozo "ngenjongo" kwaye "ngenjongo" wabangela ukwenzakala komntu, ngokutsho kwesaziso senjongo yokufuna isigwebo sokufa esifakwe kwiSithili saseMzantsi saseNew York.
Zombini ezi zityholo zinokude zibangele ukuba umntu agwetywe ukufa, ngokutsho kwaloo ncwadi yenkundla.
Kwiiveki emva kokuhlaselwa, ijaji enkulu yasemthethweni yahlasela uSaipov ngecala elimangalela ngeempazamo ezingama-22 ezaziquka izityholo ezisibhozo zokubulala ngenjongo yokuxhaphaza ulwaphulo-mthetho olulungelelanisiweyo, ezisetyenziswa ngabatshutshisi baseburhulumenteni kwiimeko zeMafia, ukongeza kwisityholo sodlame kunye nokutshatyalaliswa kwezithuthi.
Abatshutshisi bathi lo mhlaseli wawufuna "ucwangciso olukhulu nokuceba kwangaphambili" kwaye bachaze indlela uSaipov awaziphatha ngayo "njengongenalo ubuntu, okhohlakeleyo nohenyuzileyo".
"USayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov wabangela ukwenzakala, umonakalo kunye nelahleko kwiintsapho kunye nabahlobo bakaDiego Enrique Angelini, uNicholas Cleves, uAnn-Laure Decadt, uDarren Drake, uAriel Erlij, uHernan Ferruchi, uHernan Diego Mendoza noAlejandro Damian Pagnucco", ngokutsho kwesaziso sentando.
Amahlanu kulawo ayebulewe yayingabakhenkethi baseArgentina.
Sele kudlule iminyaka elishumi ukususela oko iSouthern District yaseNew York yaphakamisa ityala lesigwebo sokufa.
Ummangalelwa, uKhalid Barnes, wagwetywa ngokubulala abathengisi beziyobisi ababini kodwa ekugqibeleni wagwetywa ubomi bakhe bonke ngoSeptemba 2009.
Ekugqibeleni isigwebo sokufa senziwa kwityala laseNew York ngowe-1953 kuJulius noEthel Rosenberg, isibini esitshatileyo esabulawa emva kokuba sigwetyelwe ukuzama ukwenza imisebenzi yobuntlola kwiSoviet Union ngexesha leMfazwe Yomlomo kwiminyaka emibini ngaphambili.
Bobabini uRosenbergs bafa kwisitulo sombane ngoJuni 19, 1953.
Ngokutsho kweencwadi zenkundla, uSaipov, odabuka eUzbekistan, akazange abonakalise ukuzisola kwiintsuku neenyanga emva kokuhlaselwa.
Amapolisa athi waxelela abaphandi ukuba wayeziva kakuhle ngento awayenzayo.
Ngokutsho kweleta yetyala, uSaipov waxelela abasemagunyeni ukuba waphefumlelwa ukuba aphumelele ukuhlasela emva kokubona iividiyo ze-ISIS kwifowuni yakhe.
Ngokutsho kwamapolisa, wacela ukuba kufakwe iflegi ye-ISIS kwigumbi lakhe lasesibhedlele.
Uvumile ukuba akanatyala kwizityholo ezingama-22 zokungaziphathi kakuhle.
UDavid Patton, omnye wabameli bakawonkewonke abasemthethweni abamele uSaipov, wathi "babephoxekile" sisigqibo somtshutshisi.
"Sicinga ukuba isigqibo sokufuna isigwebo sokufa, endaweni yokwamkela isigwebo sentambo yobomi bonke ngaphandle kokukhululwa, siya kuqhubeka nokudandatheka kwezi ziganeko kubo bonke abantu ababandakanyekayo", watsho uPatton.
Iqela lakhe labameli lacela ukuba ababekhuthaza ukuba kungafunwa isigwebo sokufa.
Ilungu lePalamente leConservative Party lithi uNigel Farage ufanele abekwe ukuba abe ngumongameli weentetho zeBrexit
UNigel Farage uthembise "ukuhlanganisa imikhosi yabantu" namhlanje ngexesha loqhankqalazo kwinkomfa yeqela leTserver.
Owayesakuba yinkokheli yeUKIP uthe abezopolitiko kufuneka "bave uxinzelelo lwabantu abangakholelwa kwi-euro" xa elinye ilungu lePalamente likaTheresa May lathi kufuneka akhokele uthethathethwano ne-EU.
UMphathiswa ongenguye umQhubi uPeter Bone wathi eBirmingham ukuba iUnited Kingdom sele ingekho kwi-EU ukuba uMnu Farage unguNobhala weBrexit.
Kodwa umngeni uMrs May ajamelana nawo ekudibaniseni amaqela awo ahlukeneyo ubonakele xa amaConservative amele umanyano ahlanganisana komnye umngcelele we-Brexit eLand City.
Inkulumbuso ilwela ukugcina isicwangciso sayo sokuthethathethana seChequers phakathi kweentlaselo zabasekeli beBrexit, abasekeli bomanyano kunye ne-EU.
Amahlakani athi uza kuphumelela ukufikelela kwisivumelwano neBrussels nangona iimpendulo zithi hayi kwaye acinezela ama-euro-skeptics kunye neqela lama-conservative ukuba bakhethe phakathi kwepakethi yabo kunye nengxokolo.
U-Bone wathi kwintlanganiso yase-Leave Means Leave yase-Solihull wayefuna ukuyicima i-Chequers Compromise.
Wacebisa ukuba uMnu Farage kufuneka enziwe ilungu leNdlu yeeNkosi kwaye kufuneka anikwe uxanduva lweengxoxo neBrussels.
'Ukuba ebephethe, besingaphuma,' watsho.
Ilungu lePalamente uWellingborough wongezelela wathi: "Ndiza kuyimela iBrexit, kodwa kufuneka siwuyeke umnqophiso weChequers".
Ukucacisa inkcaso yakhe kwi-EU, wongeze wathi: "Asizange silwe iimfazwe zehlabathi ukuze sibe ngabakhonzi.
Sifuna ukwenza imithetho yethu kwilizwe lethu".
UMnu Bone wazikhaba ngaw' omane iingcebiso zokuba uluvo loluntu lutshintshile ukususela kwindibano yowama-2016: "Ingcamango yokuba abantu baseBritani batshintshe iingqondo zabo kwaye bafuna ukuhlala apha bubuxoki ngokupheleleyo".
Umxhasi we-Brexit u-Andrea Jenkyns naye waya emngcelele waza wathi kwiintatheli: "Ndiyakuxelela, Ndunankulu, ukuba abantu baphulaphule".
"Isicwangciso sikaChequers asithandwa luluntu ngokubanzi, abachasi abayi kuvotelwa sona, asithandwa liqela lethu kunye namashishini ethu, abantu abaphuma baye esitratweni baze basenze siphumelele kunyulo.
Yekani ukuzibophelela kwiChess, nize niqalise ukuphulaphula".
Kwincwadi awayibhalela uMrs. May, wongezelela wathi: "Oosiba-mongameli bayayigcina imisebenzi yabo xa begcina izithembiso zabo".
UMnu Farage wathi abezopolitiko ababekuloo ndibano kufuneka bazive benyanzelekile ukuba bafuna ukujika isigqibo esenziwe kwireferensi yango-2016.
"Oku, ngoku, ngumcimbi wokuthembana phakathi kwethu (abantu) kunye nodidi lwethu lwezopolitiko", watsho.
"Bazama ukubetha iBrexit kwaye namhlanje silapha ukuze sibaxelele ukuba asiyi kubavumela".
Xa wayethetha nesihlwele esasinemincili, wongezelela wathi: "Ndifuna ukuba nenze ukuba abezopolitiko, abaza kukrexeza ngeBrexit, bazive bexinekile".
"Sifaka umkhosi wabantu kweli lizwe elisinike uloyiso ngeBrexit kwaye asiyi kuphumla de sibe yi-UK ezimeleyo, ezimeleyo nelizukileyo".
Okwangoku, abaxhasi bomanyano bathabatha uhambo oluya eBirmingham ngaphambi kokuba babambe intlanganiso yeeyure ezimbini kumbindi wesixeko.
Inani elincinane lamashishini aphakamisa iibhanile ezibhekiselele kumaTory amelene neBrexit emva kokumiliselwa kweqela kule mpelaveki.
Ilungu leConservative leNdlu yeeNkosi u-Lord Adonis wahlekisa ngamaConservatives malunga neengxaki zokhuseleko abajamelana nazo nge-app yeqela ekuqaleni kwenkomfa.
"Aba ngabantu abathi banokuba neenkqubo ze-IT eziyimfuneko nayo yonke iteknoloji yesivumelwano seCanada plus plus, umda ongenabungozi, urhwebo olukhululekileyo olungena mida eIreland", wongezelela.
"Yinto nje engenakwenzeka.
Akukho ndlela yokhetho lweBrexit elungileyo", wongeze watsho.
