Indlela imfazwe yorhwebo yase-US-China enokuyinceda ngayo iPeking
Iimvaba zokuqala zemfazwe yorhwebo phakathi kweUnited States neTshayina zazinomsindo, yaye nangona ingathi imfazwe ayizukuphela ngokukhawuleza, iingcali zithi ukufuduka kwamazwe kunokuyinceda iBeijing kwixesha elide.
UMongameli waseUnited States uDonald Trump wakhupha isilumkiso sakhe sokuqala ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka, xa wafaka irhafu kwizinto eziphambili ezithunyelwa eChina, njengeepaneli zelanga, intsimbi nealuminiyam.
Eyona nto ibalulekileyo yenzeka kule veki, xa kwabekwa irhafu entsha kwiimveliso ezixabisa i-200.000 yezigidigidi zeerandi.
I-Beijing iye yahlasela kwakhona ngendlela efanayo, kutshanje inyuse amaxabiso ukusuka kuma-5 ekhulwini ukuya kuma-10 ekhulwini kwiimpahla zaseMerika ezixabisa i-60 lamawaka ezigidi zeerandi.
I-China izibophelele ekuxeliseni i-US kwaye i-China, owonaqoqosho lukhulu wesibini emhlabeni, ayinakuguquka ngokukhawuleza.
Ukuyekisa iWashington kuthetha ukuyekelela kwiimfuno ezithile, kodwa ukuqubuda esidlangalaleni eMelika bekuya kuba yinto ehlazo kakhulu kuXi Jinping, uMongameli waseTshayina.
Sekunjalo, iingcali zithi, ukuba iPeking idlala kakuhle amakhadi ayo, uxinzelelo lwemfazwe yorhwebo neUnited States lunokuyinceda iChina kwixesha elide ngokunciphisa ukuxhomekeka koqoqosho lwezo mbini.
UAbhigail Grace, oyingcali yeAsia kwiCenter for New American Security uthi: "Imbono yokuba isigqibo sezopolitiko esenziwa ngokukhawuleza eWashington okanye eBeijing sinokudala iimeko ezibangela ukuwa kwelizwe ngalinye, iyingozi kakhulu kunoko bekucingelwa ngamangqina".
ISyria 'ikulungele' ukubuyisela iimbacu, utsho uMphathiswa Wezangaphandle
ISyria ithi ilungele ukubuya kwababaleki ngokuzithandela kwaye ifuna uncedo ukuze iphinde yakhe ilizwe, elihlaselwe yimfazwe yeminyaka engaphezu kwesixhenxe.
