"Ngoku imeko yasesitalatweni izinzile kwaye ikhuselekile, ngenxa yenkqubela eyenziweyo ekulweni nobugrogrisi", utshilo.
Urhulumente uqhubeka nokuhlaziya iindawo ezonakaliswe ziintlola ukuze abuyisele ubomi obuqhelekileyo.
Zonke iimeko zokubuyela ngokuzithandela kwilizwe leembacu ezanyanzeleka ukuba zifudukele kwelinye ilizwe ngenxa yobunqolobi kunye namanyathelo ezoqoqosho angamalungu amabini achaphazela ubomi bazo bemihla ngemihla kunye nokondliwa kwazo ziyafezekiswa.
