Iqela laseYurophu lifumana uloyiso kwiRyder Cup eParis
Iqela laseYurophu liphumelele kwiNdebe yeRyder ka-2018 ngokutshaya iqela laseMerika ngenqaku lokugqibela le-16.5 ukuya kwi-10.5 eLe Golf National, ngaphandle kweParis, eFrance.
I-USA sele ilahlekelwe amaxesha amathandathu alandelelanayo kumhlaba waseYurophu kwaye ayizange iphumelele iRyder Cup eYurophu ukususela ngonyaka we-1993.
Iqela laseYurophu laphinda lazuza isithsaba xa iqela likaputeni waseDenmark uThomas Bjorn's lafikelela kumanqaku ali-14.5 afunekayo ukoyisa iUnited States.
Inkwenkwezi yaseMerika uPhil Mickelson, owayesilwa ixesha elininzi lomdlalo, wakhaba isibhamu sokuphuma emanzini kumngxuma we par 3 16, nto leyo eyayinika uFrancesco Molinari uloyiso.
Umdlali wegalufa waseTaliyane uMolinari waqaqamba kuzo zonke iiseti zakhe waza waba ngomnye wabadlali abane abaye bafumana i-5-0-0 ukusukela oko kwaqala ubume bale tumente ngo-1979.
UmMerika uJordan Spieth wabekwa ecaleni nge-5&4 ngumdlali ongekho mgangathweni weqela laseYurophu uThorbjorn Olesen, waseDenmark.
Oyena mdlali uqeqeshiweyo emhlabeni, uDustin Johnson, waphulukana no-2 no-1 noIan Poulter waseNgilani, owayenokudlala iRyder Cup yakhe yokugqibela.
Umgcini weRyder Cups ezisibhozo, uSpeyin Sergio Garcia, waba ngoyena uphumelele kakhulu kulo msitho, ngamanqaku angama-25.5 omsebenzi.
"Andisoloko ndilila, kodwa namhlanje andinakukwazi ukuzibamba.
Kuye kwaba ngunyaka onzima.
Enkosi, Thomas, ngokundinyula nangokukholelwa kum.
Ndivuya gqitha kuba ndiyifumene indebe yam.
Iqela lelona libalulekileyo... kwaye ndiyavuya kuba ndikwazile ukunceda", utshilo uGarcia emva kokuphumelela eYurophu.
Udlulisela umxokelelwano kwilizwe lakhe uJohn Ram, owatshayela ingqungquthela yegalufa yaseMntla Melika uTiger Woods 2&1 kukhuphiswano lomntu ngamnye ngeCawa.
"Ndizingca ngokumangalisayo ngokuba ndiphumelele uTiger Woods, ndakhula ndimlandela", watsho uRahm, oneminyaka engama-23.
UWoods waphulukana nemidlalo emine awayenayo eFrance kwaye ngoku unerekhodi yomsebenzi kwiRyder Cup ka 13-21-3.
Eli linani elingaqhelekanga lomnye wabadlali ababalaseleyo abakhe baphila, ophumelele iimbasa ezili-14 ezinkulu, ephantsi nje koJack Nicklaus.
Iqela laseMerika lalisilwa yonke impelaveki ukuze lifune izitalato, ngaphandle kukaPatrick Reed, Justin Thomas noTony Finau, abadlala igalufa ekumgangatho ophezulu kulo lonke ukhuphiswano.
Umdlali ophambili waseMerika uJim Furyk wathetha emva komdlalo wokuphelelwa lithemba weqela lakhe: "Ndiyazingca ngala madoda, alwe nzima.
Kule ntsasa, bekukho ixesha apho besicinezela iqela laseYurophu.
Sasilwa.
Ndiyikhulula iminqwazi yam kuThomas.
Ungumphathi omkhulu.
Abadlali bayo abali-12 badlale kakuhle.
Siza kuhlangana kwakhona, sisebenze nePGA yaseMelika kunye neKomiti yethu yeNdebe yeRyder kwaye siqhubele phambili.
Ndibathanda aba badlali abali-12 yaye ndiyazingca ngokuba ngumphathi wabo.
