Ukuhlaziywa komjelo obomvu: iziphumo zincipha ePinellas, Manatee naseSarasota
Ingxelo yakutshanje yeFlorida Fish and Wildlife Commission ibonisa ukuncitshiswa ngokubanzi kwezinto ezibomvu kwiindawo ezithile zaseTampa Bay.
Ngokwe-FWC, iimeko zokwanda ezixhaphakileyo ziyaxelwa kwiindawo zasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte naseCollier, nto leyo ebonisa ukuba kukho uxinzelelo oluphantsi.
Ukuxhaphaka komlambo obomvu kuqhubeka malunga neekhilomitha ezingama-200 zonxweme, ukusuka kumantla ePinellas ukuya kumazantsi e-Lee counties.
Kukho amabala anokufunyanwa kumgama oziikhilomitha ezili-16 ukusuka kunxweme lwelizwe laseHillsborough, kodwa kwiindawo ezimbalwa kunakwimeko yeveki ephelileyo.
Kwakhona kwabonwa umlambo obomvu kwiphondo lasePasco.
Kuye kwaxelwa ukuba kukho iingqungquthela eziphakathi kunxweme okanye kude kunxweme e Pinellas County kule veki iphelileyo, iingqungquthela eziphantsi ukuya phezulu kunxweme e Hillsborough County, iingqungquthela ezantsi okanye phezulu kunxweme e Manatee County, iingqungquthela ezantsi ukuya phakathi kunxweme e Charlotte County, iingqungquthela ezantsi kunxweme okanye kude kunxweme e Lee County, kunye neengqungquthela ezisezantsi kunxweme e Collier County.
Ukuphazamiseka komoya kuyaqhubeka ukuchazwa kwiphondo lasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee naseCollier.
Akukho ngxaki yokuphefumla eye yachazwa kwiveki ephelileyo kumantla mpuma eFlorida.
